%2021%2C187%20to%2010%2C179%2C%20with%20winning%20candidate%20Sarah%20Dyke%20hailing%20a%20%26quot%3Bstunning%20and%20historic%20victory%26quot%3B%20and%20taking%20aim%20at%20the%20%26quot%3Bwoeful%20government%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20have%20been%20let%20down%20and%20taken%20for%20granted.%20This%20government%20is%20too%20busy%20being%20a%20circus%20of%20chaos%20--%20enough%20is%20enough%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Tories%20had%20also%20been%20expected%20to%20lose%20Johnson's%20former%20seat%20of%20Uxbridge%20and%20South%20Ruislip%2C%20but%20won%20by%2013%2C965%20votes%20to%2013%2C470%2C%20delivering%20a%20blow%20to%20Labour%20leader%20Keir%20Starmer%20and%20London's%20Labour%20mayor%20Sadiq%20Khan.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWinning%20candidate%20Steve%20Tuckwell%20said%20the%20%26quot%3Bnumber%20one%26quot%3B%20issue%20had%20been%20Khan's%20expansion%20of%20a%20tax%20on%20polluting%20vehicles%20to%20outer%20London%20boroughs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20Labour%20MPs%20in%20similar%20seats%20%26quot%3Bwill%20now%20be%20panicking%26quot%3B%20and%20the%20result%20is%20likely%20to%20spark%20conversations%20between%20Starmer%20and%20Khan.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E'Local%20issues'%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20heavy%20defeats%20in%20the%20other%20two%20contests%20leave%20Sunak%20increasingly%20vulnerable%20ahead%20of%20next%20year's%20likely%20general%20election%2C%20with%20parliament's%20six-week%20break%20providing%20welcome%20relief.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20main%20opposition%20Labour%20party%20are%20currently%20enjoying%20double-digit%20poll%20leads%20and%20are%20poised%20to%20retake%20power%20for%20the%20first%20time%20in%20over%20a%20decade.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20has%20now%20won%20six%20by-elections%20since%20March%20last%20year%2C%20with%20two%20of%20those%20seats%20captured%20from%20the%20Tories.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Uxbridge%20and%20South%20Ruislip%20contest%20was%20triggered%20after%20the%20scandal-tarred%20Johnson%20resigned%20as%20an%20MP%20last%20month.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20quit%20after%20learning%20that%20a%20cross-party%20parliamentary%20committee%20had%20concluded%20he%20deliberately%20lied%20to%20lawmakers%20about%20lockdown-breaking%20parties%20during%20the%20Covid%20pandemic%2C%20and%20recommended%20a%2090-day%20suspension.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20much%20attention%20had%20been%20on%20Johnson%2C%20voter%20Deborah%20Willott%2C%2065%2C%20told%20AFP%3A%20%26quot%3BIt's%20a%20by-election%20so%20it's%20really%20focused%20on%20the%20local%20issues%20much%20more%20than%20if%20it%20was%20a%20general%20election%2C%26quot%3B%20as%20she%20cast%20her%20ballot%20in%20a%20church%20polling%20site.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJohnson's%20ally%20Nigel%20Adams%20quit%20shortly%20afterwards%20after%20failing%20to%20be%20nominated%20for%20a%20peerage%2C%20triggering%20the%20Selby%20and%20Ainsty%20by-election.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20third%20vote%20in%20Somerton%20and%20Frome%20was%20called%20after%20its%20Tory%20MP%20David%20Warburton%20stood%20down%20following%20an%20admission%20of%20cocaine%20use.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESunak%2C%20who%20has%20not%20been%20visible%20on%20the%20campaign%20trail%2C%20sought%20to%20project%20a%20business-as-usual%20image%20Thursday%20but%20privately%20briefed%20backbench%20MPs%20to%20expect%20the%20worst.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ESunak%20struggles%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESunak%20became%20prime%20minister%20following%20the%20disastrous%2044-day%20tenure%20of%20predecessor%20Liz%20Truss%20and%20initially%20succeeded%20in%20stabilising%20financial%20markets%20panicked%20by%20her%20radical%20tax-slashing%20agenda.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20the%2043-year-old%20former%20finance%20minister%20has%20struggled%20to%20reverse%20his%20party's%20declining%20fortunes%2C%20which%20first%20set%20in%20during%20the%20so-called%20%26quot%3BPartygate%26quot%3B%20scandal%20under%20Johnson.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESunak's%20turnaroun