22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fvariety.com%2F%3Fp%3D1235673190%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Britney%C2%A0Spears%20is%20getting%20back%20to%20the%20music%20%E2%80%94%20again.%20The%20Princess%20of%20Pop%20and%20her%20frequent%20collaborator%2C%20Will.i.am%2C%20have%20dropped%20a%20new%20single%2C%20%E2%80%9CMind%20Your%20Business%2C%E2%80%9D%20which%20is%20the%20second%20song%20to%20be%20released%20after%20her%2013-year%20conservatorship%20was%20terminated.%20%E2%80%9CMind%20Your%20Business%E2%80%9D%20marks%20the%20first%20reunion%20for%20Spears%20and%20Will.i.am%20since%20their%20triple-platinum%20hit%20%5B%E2%80%A6%5D%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Elizabeth%20Wagmeister%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fvariety.com%2F2023%2Fmusic%2Fnews%2Fbritney-spears-will-i-am-song-mind-your-business-1235673190%2F%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fvariety-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fvariety.com%2F2023%2Fmusic%2Fnews%2Fbritney-spears-will-i-am-song-mind-your-business-1235673190%2Famp%2F%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fvariety.com%2F2023%2Fmusic%2Fnews%2Fbritney-spears-will-i-am-song-mind-your-business-1235673190%2Famp%2F%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Most%20MSMEs%20Are%20Not%20Even%20in%20the%20Policy%20Net%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F21093307%2FIndia_-_Varanasi_electric_fan_factory_-_1464.jpeg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20micro%2C%20small%20and%20medium%20enterprises%20(MSMEs)%20sector%20contributes%20nearly%2045%25%20of%20the%20country%E2%80%99s%20industrial%20output%20and%2040%25%20of%20its%20exports.%20Despite%20their%20significance%2C%20the%20MSMEs%E2%80%99%20challenges%20have%20only%20increased%20for%20three%20reasons%3A%20demonetisation%2C%20followed%20by%20some%20degree%20of%20forced%20%E2%80%98formalisation%E2%80%99%20(of%20sorts)%20due%20to%20GST%2C%20and%20then%20an%20ill-planned%20lockdown%20of%20unnecessarily%20harsh%20strictness%2C%20needlessly%20national%20in%20scope%20(March%202020%2C%20when%20there%20were%20less%20than%20600%20Covid%20cases).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFirst%2C%20how%20many%20MSMEs%20are%20really%20under%20the%20policy%20lens%3F%20Schemes%2C%20subsidies%20or%20new%20policy%20initiatives%20like%20Emergency%20Credit%20Line%20Guarantee%20Scheme%20(ECLGS)%2C%20Prime%20Minister%E2%80%99s%20Employment%20Generation%20Programme%20(PMEGP)%2C%20Credit%20Guarantee%20Fund%20Trust%20for%20Micro%20and%20Small%20Enterprises%20(CGTMSE)%2C%20Micro%20and%20Small%20Enterprises%20Cluster%20Development%20Programme%20(MSE-CDP)%20and%20Scheme%20of%20Fund%20for%20Regeneration%20of%20Traditional%20Industries%20(SFURTI)%20are%20for%20registered%20enterprises.%20When%20the%20Centre%20talks%20about%20new%20schemes%2C%20subsidies%20or%20policy%20initiatives%2C%20it%20is%20merely%20supporting%20those%20registered%20enterprises.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHow%20many%20MSMEs%20are%20registered%3F%20It%E2%80%99s%20not%20very%20clear.%20After%20the%20implementation%20of%20the%20Micro%2C%20Small%20%26amp%3B%20Medium%20Enterprises%20Development%20(MSMED)%20Act%20in%202006%2C%20the%20fourth%20MSME%20census%20was%20the%20first%20to%20be%20executed%20for%20both%20registered%20and%20unregistered%20MSMEs.%20It%20found%20that%20in%202006%E2%80%9307%2C%201.55%20million%20MSMEs%20were%20registered%2C%205.9%25%20of%20the%2026.1%20million%20MSMEs%20active%20at%20that%20time.%20That%20was%20the%20last%20census.%20Moreover%2C%20while%20the%20government%20has%20conducted%20the%207th%20Economic%20Census%20in%202019%2C%20which%20could%20reveal%20changes%20in%20the%20state%20of%20MSMES%20between%202013%20(6th%C2%A0Economic%20Census)%20and%202019%2C%20that%20data%20has%20not%20been%20made%20public.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Development%20Gone%20'Rogue'%20and%20the%20High%20Flood%20in%20Delhi%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fenvironment%2Fdevelopment-rogue-flood-delhi%5C%22%3EDevelopment%20Gone%20%E2%80%98Rogue%E2%80%99%20and%20the%20High%20Flood%20in%20Delhi%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThough%20the%20National%20Sample%20Survey%20(NSS)%20conducts%20the%20Unincorporated%20Non-Agricultural%20Enterprises%20(Excluding%20Construction)%20sample%20survey%20in%20a%20five-year%20interval%2C%20the%20latest%20one%20is%20the%2073rd%20round%20in%202015%E2%80%9316.%20According%20to%20the%2073rd%C2%A0round%20NSS%20data%2C%20only%2030%25%20of%20the%20total%20estimated%2063%20million%20MSMEs%20were%20registered%2C%20which%20is%20not%20a%20bad%20number%20for%20the%20informal%20sector.%20But%20it%20took%20decades%20to%20get%20to%20this.%20NSS%20collected%20this%20data%20on%20registration%20under%20a%20list%20of%20acts%20and%20authorities.%20Surprisingly%2C%20this%20list%20did%20not%20include%20the%20MSMED%20Act%2C%202006%2C%20or%20MSME%20registration.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFurthermore%2C%20registration%20under%20these%20acts%20or%20authorities%20of%20MSMEs%20is%20a%20mere%20formality.%20It%20is%20also%20not%20synonymous%20with%20formalisation.%20These%20acts%20or%20bodies%20only%20register%20about%2030%25%20of%20unorganised%20firms.%20Formalisation%20under%20Factories%20Act%20registration%20assures%20social%20security%20benefits%20and%20other%20benefits%20to%20the%20firms%2C%20but%20registration%20under%20other%20acts%20or%20authorities%20changes%20nothing.%20The%20introduction%20to%20the%207th%C2%A0Economic%20Census%20states%20that%20its%20objective%20would%20be%20to%20create%20an%20Indian%C2%A0%20business%20registry.%20That%20still%20seems%20a%20far%20cry%20in%20the%20wilderness.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20major%20hurdle%20for%20MSMEs%20is%20the%20cumbersome%20process%20of%20registering%20with%20government%20agencies.%20Currently%2C%20MSMEs%20need%20to%20register%20under%20various%20schemes%20such%20as%20GST%2C%20the%20Ministry%20of%20Corporate%20Affairs%20and%20Udyam.%20This%20adds%20to%20their%20administrative%20burden%20and%20also%20creates%20confusion%20and%20duplication%20of%20effort.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20July%202020%2C%20the%20government%20launched%20the%20Udyam%20registration%20portal%20as%20a%20unified%20platform%20for%20MSMEs%20to%20register%20and%20obtain%20various%20certifications.%20However%2C%20the%20number%20of%20MSMEs%20which%20did%20so%20remains%20meagre%20%E2%80%95%2014.3%20million.%20This%20is%20a%20fraction%20of%20the%20estimated%2063%20million%20MSMEs%20in%20the%20country%20in%202015-16%20(NSO).%20But%20this%20data%20is%20also%20too%20old%20to%20use%20because%20the%2073rd%C2%A0NSS%20survey%20round%20(2015-16)%20used%20the%20fifth%20Economic%20Census%20(2005)%20as%20the%20sampling%20frame.%20We%20don%E2%80%99t%20even%20have%20any%20comprehensive%20regular%20database%20to%20monitor%20the%20second%20largest%20sector%20after%20agriculture.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22'There%20Are%20No%20Jobs%20in%20Our%20Village'%3A%20Rising%20Costs%2C%20Stagnating%20Wages%20Exacerbate%20Rural%20Distress%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flabour%2Fthere-are-no-jobs-in-our-village-rising-costs-stagnating-wages-exacerbate-rural-distress%5C%22%3E%E2%80%98There%20Are%20No%20Jobs%20in%20Our%20Village%E2%80%99%3A%20Rising%20Costs%2C%20Stagnating%20Wages%20Exacerbate%20Rural%20Distress%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPoor%20registration%20raises%20issues%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E1)%20A%20significant%20portion%20of%20MSMEs%20in%20India%20are%20not%20on%20the%20books%20and%20operate%20in%20the%20informal%20sector.%20They%20may%20prefer%20to%20remain%20unregistered%20to%20avoid%20regulatory%20scrutiny%2C%20taxes%20and%20compliance.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E2)%20After%20registering%2C%20MSMEs%20have%20to%20comply%20with%20various%20statutory%20requirements%2C%20such%20as%20maintaining%20books%20of%20accounts%2C%20filing%20returns%20and%20adhering%20to%20laws%2Frules.%20This%20could%20be%20daunting%20for%20small%20business%20owners%20without%20the%20resources%20to%20hire%20professionals%20for%20compliance.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E3)%20While%20MSMEs%20in%20India%20are%20eligible%20for%20several%20incentives%20such%20as%20subsidies%2C%20tax%20benefits%20and%20credit%20guarantees%2C%20many%20small%20business%20owners%20may%20not%20find%20these%20significant%20enough%20to%20justify%20the%20registration%20process.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E4)%20Lack%20of%20awareness%20among%20MSMEs%20about%20the%20importance%20of%20registration%20and%20its%20benefits.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E5)%20At%20present%2C%20the%20process%20involves%20obtaining%20multiple%20registrations%2C%20such%20as%20for%20GST%2C%20Udyam%20and%20other%20state-specific%20registrations.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20addition%2C%20the%20government%20must%20also%20ensure%20that%20the%20benefits%20of%20registration%20that%20reach%20MSMEs%20exceed%20the%20costs.%20Easy%20access%20to%20credit%2C%20infrastructure%20support%20and%20a%20simplified%20tax%20regime%20would%20help.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3ESantosh%20%3Cspan%3EMehrotra%3C%2Fspan%3E%20is%20Professorial%20Fellow%2C%20Nehru%20Memorial%20Museum%20%26amp%3B%20Library%20and%20Tuhinsubhra%20Giri%20is%20Fellow%20at%20Research%20and%20Information%20System%20for%20Developing%20Countries.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1689912324000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F21093307%2FIndia_-_Varanasi_electric_fan_factory_-_1464.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Feconomy%2Fmost-msmes-are-not-even-in-the-policy-net%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Despite%20their%20significance%2C%20the%20MSMEs%E2%80%99%20challenges%20have%20only%20increased%20for%20three%20reasons%3A%20demonetisation%2C%20followed%20by%20some%20degree%20of%20forced%20%E2%80%98formalisation%E2%80%99%20(of%20sorts)%20due%20to%20GST%2C%20and%20then%20an%20ill-planned%20lockdown%20of%20unnecessarily%20harsh%20strictness.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Feconomy%2Fmost-msmes-are-not-even-in-the-policy-net%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Mount%20Kailash%20To%20Become%20Accessible%20From%20India%20September%20Onwards%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EFrom%20September%20this%20year%2C%20devotees%20will%20be%20able%20to%20visit%20Mount%20Kailash%2C%20believed%20to%20be%20the%20abode%20of%20Lord%20Shiva%2C%20from%20the%20Indian%20territory.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOfficials%20said%20that%20the%20Border%20Roads%20Organisation%20(BRO)%20has%20started%20the%20work%20on%20cutting%20the%20road%20from%20KMVN%20Huts%20in%20Nabhidhang%20in%20Pithoragarh%20district%20to%20Lipulekh%20pass%20on%20the%20India-China%20border%2C%20which%20will%20be%20completed%20by%20September.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EVimal%20Goswami%2C%20Chief%20Engineer%20of%20BRO's%20Diamond%20Project%2C%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BWe%20have%20started%20the%20work%20of%20cutting%20the%20road%20from%20KMVN%20Huts%20to%20Lipulekh%20Pass%20in%20Nabhidhang%2C%20about%20six%20and%20a%20half%20kilometres%20long.%26quot%3B%20After%20the%20completion%20of%20the%20road%2C%20'Kailash%20View%20Point'%20will%20be%20ready%20along%20the%20road.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHirak%20Project%20has%20been%20given%20the%20responsibility%20of%20developing%20'Kailash%20View%20Point'%20by%20the%20Indian%20government.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Goswami%20said%20that%20a%20lot%20of%20road-cutting%20work%20has%20been%20done%20and%20if%20the%20weather%20is%20favourable%2C%20it%20will%20be%20completed%20by%20September.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Kailash-Mansarovar%20yatra%20through%20the%20Lipulekh%20Pass%2C%20which%20was%20postponed%20due%20to%20the%20Covid%20pandemic%2C%20has%20not%20resumed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESuch%20a%20long%20stall%20has%20contributed%20to%20the%20efforts%20by%20the%20Indian%20government%20in%20forging%20an%20alternative%20path%20for%20the%20devotees%20to%20access%20Mount%20Kailash.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(This%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff