s%20unhappy%20wife%20who%2C%20even%20as%20their%20marriage%20is%20falling%20apart%2C%20undertake%20a%20tour%20of%20World%20War%20II%20locations%2C%20including%20Anne%20Frank's%20home%20and%20an%20Auschwitz%20gas%20chamber.%20The%20longer%20their%20peregrination%20lasts%20the%20less%20sense%20it%20makes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20girl%20is%20a%20college%20topper.%20The%20guy%20is%20an%20average%20bloke%20who%20thrives%20on%20talking%20up%20his%20accomplishments.%20The%20woman's%20favourite%20writers%20are%20Tolstoy%2C%20Shakespeare%20and%20Tagore.%20The%20man%20hasn't%20graduated%20beyond%20Diamond%20Comics.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20young%20lady%20likes%20%3Ci%3EScent%20of%20a%20Woman%2C%20Life%20is%20Beautiful%3C%2Fi%3E%20and%20%3Ci%3EGood%20Will%20Hunting%3C%2Fi%3E.%20The%20husband%20is%20into%20%3Ci%3EJurassic%20Park%2C%20Spiderman%3C%2Fi%3E%20and%20%3Ci%3ETitanic%3C%2Fi%3E%20when%20he%20isn't%20consuming%20%3Ci%3EHero%20No.%201%2C%20Jodi%20No.1%3C%2Fi%3E%20and%20%3Ci%3EAunty%20No.%201%3C%2Fi%3E.%20A%20world%20separates%20the%20two.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETen%20months%20into%20a%20marriage%20that%20is%20going%20nowhere%2C%20the%20man%2C%20his%20wife%20in%20tow%20against%20his%20wish%2C%20flies%20to%20Europe%20to%20brush%20up%20on%20his%20knowledge%20of%20World%20War%20II.%20Like%20the%20film%2C%20the%20voyage%20hops%20from%20point%20to%20point%20without%20making%20any%20point%20that%20could%20be%20regarded%20as%20genuinely%20revelatory.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ciframe%20allowfullscreen%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fembed%2FNyeG2mLVCS4%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22560%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22YouTube%20video%20player%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22315%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20%3Ci%3EBawaal%3C%2Fi%3E%20story%20is%20credited%20to%20Ashwiny%20Iyer%20Tiwari%20and%20the%20screenplay%20to%20four%20writers%20(Nikhil%20Mehrotra%2C%20Shreyas%20Jain%2C%20Piyush%20Gupta%20and%20the%20director).%20What%20the%20team%20delivers%20is%20an%20anodyne%2C%20half-baked%20thesis%20on%20war%20that%20equates%20the%20wages%20of%20military%20conflict%20with%20the%20emotional%20price%20of%20not%20giving%20a%20marriage%20a%20chance%20to%20stabilise%20itself.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMarred%20by%20a%20wobbly%20script%20and%20uninspired%20execution%2C%20%3Ci%3EBawaal%3C%2Fi%3E%20is%20an%20escapist%20movie%20would%20have%20passed%20muster%20has%20it%20not%20bordered%20on%20the%20mendacious%20the%20way%20it%20does.%20It%20seeks%20to%20divert%20the%20attention%20of%20the%20audience%20from%20the%20miseries%20and%20scares%20that%20are%20looming%20over%20the%20modern%20world%20and%20urge%20them%20to%20cast%20their%20minds%20all%20the%20way%20back%20to%20the%20atrocities%20that%20the%20Nazis%20committed%20in%20Europe%20over%20eight%20decades%20ago.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDo%20we%2C%20given%20the%20times%20that%20we%20live%20in%2C%20need%20to%20go%20so%20far%20back%20in%20time%20in%20order%20to%20construct%20a%20commentary%20on%20mankind's%20propensity%20to%20run%20itself%20into%20the%20ground%3F%20It%20smacks%20of%20overt%20artifice.%20The%20film's%20critical%20plot%20points%20are%20so%20contrived%20that%20the%20last%20thing%20that%20one%20would%20be%20able%20to%20do%20is%20defend%20them%20by%20the%20means%20of%20logic.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAjay%20%26quot%3BAjju%26quot%3B%20Dikshit%20(Varun%20Dhawan)%20is%20a%20school%20teacher%20whose%20heart%20isn't%20in%20the%20job.%20Dissatisfied%20with%20his%20lot%20in%20life%2C%20he%20lies%20left%20and%20right%20because%20he%20does%20not%20want%20the%20world%20to%20know%20how%20much%20of%20a%20loser%20he%20is.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20tall%20tales%20that%20Ajju%20trots%20out%20to%20his%20students%20about%20his%20imaginary%20feats%20have%20takers%20all%20across%20Lucknow%2C%20the%20audience%20is%20airily%20told%20via%20a%20voiceover.%20Either%20the%20whole%20city%20is%20hopelessly%20gullible%20or%20our%20guy%20is%20a%20dissembler%20who%20can%20do%20no%20wrong.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20Ajju%20marries%20a%20comely%20achiever%20Nisha%20(Janhvi%20Kapoor)%2C%20he%20chooses%20to%20cold-shoulder%20her%20completely%20because%20she%20has%20a%20medical%20condition%20that%20he%20finds%20embarrassing.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20Ajju%20runs%20into%20trouble%20with%20a%20legislator%20(Mukesh%20Tiwari)%20and%20is%20suspended%20by%20the%20school%20for%20a%20month%20pending%20an%20inquiry%20into%20his%20conduct%2C%20he%20decides%20to%20make%20a%20trip%20to%20various%20World%20War%20II%20sites%20and%20deliver%20video%20lectures%20to%20his%20students%20from%20the%20spot.%20He%20thinks%20that%20would%20be%20a%20good%20way%20to%20turn%20public%20opinion%20in%20his%20favour.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20also%20pulls%20a%20fast%20one%20on%20his%20bank-employee%20father%20(Manoj%20Pahwa).%20He%20feigns%20that%20his%20wife%20will%20be%20accompanying%20him%20to%20Europe%20because%20only%20then%20is%20his%20dad%20likely%20to%20fund%20the%20expensive%20trip.%20The%20neglected%20Nisha%20learns%20in%20the%20nick%20of%20time%20what%20Ajju%20is%20up%20to.%20She%20scuttles%20his%20ploy%20to%20cut%20her%20out%20of%20his%20travel%20plans.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20European%20sojourn%2C%20which%20sees%20Nisha%20and%20Ajju%20visiting%20Paris%2C%20Normandy%2C%20Amsterdam%2C%20Berlin%20and%20Auschwitz%2C%20throws%20the%20couple%20into%20unforeseen%20situations%20that%20bring%20to%20light%20the%20stern%20mettle%20that%20Nisha%20is%20made%20of.%20A%20few%20of%20the%20run-ins%2C%20especially%20an%20extended%20one%20involving%20a%20Gujarati%20family%20on%20the%20same%20flight%20as%20them%2C%20are%20supposed%20to%20evoke%20mirth.%20They%20do%2C%20but%20not%20quite%20with%20the%20intended%20result.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20facile%20storyline%20has%20a%20consistently%20hollow%20ring%20to%20it.%20Stretching%20the%20idea%20of%20learning%20from%20history%20and%20not%20repeating%20mistakes%20of%20the%20past%20to%20encompass%20the%20fallout%20of%20the%20Holocaust%20comes%20at%20a%20heavy%20cost%20-%20it%20robs%20%3Ci%3EBawaal%3C%2Fi%3E%20of%20any%20possibility%20of%20being%20taken%20seriously%2C%20no%20matter%20how%20morally%20outraged%20the%20makers%20might%20appear%20to%20be%20at%20what%20happened%20when%20Nazi%20Germany%20invaded%20the%20rest%20of%20Europe.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBe%20happy%20with%20what%20you've%20got%2C%20do%20not%20covet%20what%20isn't%20yours%20-%20that%20time-worn%20homily%20is%20meant%20to%20be%20the%20principal%20takeaway%20from%20%3Ci%3EBawaal%3C%2Fi%3E.%20Does%20one%20really%20need%20renewed%20edification%20couched%20in%20a%20tale%20that%20is%20part%20a%20sanctimonious%20denunciation%20of%20war%2C%20part%20an%20indictment%20of%20insensitive%2C%20self-serving%20masculinity.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIf%20not%20exactly%20screechy%2C%20%3Ci%3EBawaal%3C%2Fi%3E%20is%20horribly%20preachy.%20The%20film's%20two%20lead%20actors%2C%20notwithstanding%20the%20palpable%20enthusiasm%20that%20they%20bring%20to%20bear%20upon%20their%20roles%2C%20do%20not%20stand%20any%20chance%20of%20rising%20above%20the%20muddle.%20Janhvi%20Kapoor%20and%20Varun%20Dhawan%20go%20through%20the%20motions%20without%20ever%20finding%20a%20way%20around%20the%20dead-ends%20that%20they%20frequently%20hit%20along%20the%20way.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3EBawaal%3C%2Fi%3E%20is%20as%20fake%20as%20its%20fibber-hero%20-%20a%20film%20that%20masquerades%20as%20cinema's%20equivalent%20of%20an%20agony%20aunt%20who%20wants%20to%20mend%20a%20marriage%20on%20the%20brink%20of%20annulment%20even%20as%20its%20larger%20aim%20is%20to%20deliver%20a%20pat%20truism%20about%20man's%20inhumanity%20to%20man.%20The%20exercise%2C%20no%20matter%20how%20offbeat%20it%20seems%2C%20inevitably%20sinks%20into%20a%20bottomless%20trench.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1689911280000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-07%2Fp7ftmgh8_-bawaal_625x300_21_July_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fentertainment%2Fbawaal-review-janhvi-kapoor-varun-dhawan-stand-no-chance-of-rising-above-the