erson%20has%20survived%20on%20record%20is%203.%20I%20knew%20I%20had%20the%20strongest%20son%20in%20the%20world%2C%26quot%3B%20Ms%20Briana%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20added%2C%20%26quot%3BHe%20is%20my%20hero%20and%20I%20will%20forever%20be%20grateful%20to%20God%20for%20giving%20me%20the%20goodest%20baby%20boy%20on%20earth%2C%20and%20I%20am%20grateful%20to%20know%20I%20will%20have%20that%20boy%20in%20heaven%20someday.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20boy's%20parents%20initially%20became%20aware%20that%20something%20was%20wrong%20when%20their%20son%20started%20exhibiting%20%26quot%3Bflu-like%20symptoms%26quot%3B%20last%20week%2C%20according%20to%20a%20social%20media%20post%20by%20friends%20of%20the%20Bundy%20family.%20Ms%20Briana%20took%20him%20to%20the%20hospital%20right%20away%2C%20where%20the%20medical%20staff%20originally%20believed%20he%20had%20meningitis.%20Later%2C%20they%20discovered%20he%20had%20the%20deadly%20brain-eating%20amoeba%20that%20caused%20widespread%20concern%20earlier%20this%20year.%20It%20also%20claimed%20the%20life%20of%20a%20man%20in%20his%2050s%20in%20the%20US%20in%20February%202023.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETwo%20days%20before%20the%20incident%2C%20Ms%20Briana%20claimed%20in%20a%20Facebook%20post%20that%20the%20Centre%20for%20Disease%20Control%20and%20Prevention%20(CDC)%20had%20declined%20to%20provide%20any%20treatment%20to%20the%20two-year-old%20because%20he%20was%20%26quot%3Bpast%20the%20point%20of%20any%20survivor%26quot%3B.%20The%20health%20agency%20hasn't%20responded%20to%20her%20allegations.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccordion%20to%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cdc.gov%2Fparasites%2Fnaegleria%2Findex.html%5C%22%3ECDC%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20Naegleria%20fowleri%20is%20a%20type%20of%20amoeba%20(single-celled%20living%20organism)%20that%20is%20found%20in%20warm%20freshwater%20environments%20like%20lakes%2C%20rivers%20and%20hot%20springs.%20It%20can%20infect%20the%20brain%20when%20amoeba-containing%20water%20passes%20up%20th