said%20that%20he%20had%20flagged%20to%20his%20friend%20that%20the%20carbon%20fibre%20and%20titanium%20craft%20was%20dangerous.%20%26quot%3BHe%20definitely%20knew%20it%20was%20going%20to%20end%20like%20this.%20He%20quite%20literally%20and%20figuratively%20went%20out%20with%20the%20biggest%20bang%20in%20human%20history%20that%20you%20could%20go%20out%20with.%20He%20was%20the%20last%20person%20to%20murder%20two%20billionaires%20at%20once%20and%20have%20them%20pay%20for%20the%20privilege%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20told%20the%20outlet.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20think%20Stockton%20was%20designing%20a%20mousetrap%20for%20billionaires%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Stanley%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Stanley%20also%20shared%20his%20experience%20of%20going%20on%20a%20test%20dive%20with%20Mr%20Rush%20in%20the%20Bahamas%20in%202019.%20He%20said%20that%20he%20has%20%26quot%3Bno%20doubt%26quot%3B%20in%20his%20mind%20and%20believes%20that%20%26quot%3Bit%20was%20the%20carbon%20fibre%20tube%20that%20was%20the%20mechanical%20part%20that%20failed%26quot%3B%20which%20led%20to%20the%20implosion%20of%20Titan.%20%26quot%3BEvery%20three%20to%20four%20minutes%20there%20were%20loud%20gunshot-like%20noises.%20It's%20a%20heck%20of%20a%20sound%20to%20hear%20when%20you%20are%20that%20far%20under%20the%20ocean%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20per%20Mr%20Stanley%2C%20he%20expressed%20his%20worries%20to%20his%20friend%20about%20the%20carbon%20fibre%20hull%20of%20the%20vessel%20%26quot%3Bbreaking%20down%2C%26quot%3B%20telling%20him%20that%20%26quot%3Bit%20will%20only%20get%20worse%26quot%3B%20in%20a%20series%20of%20furious%20calls%20and%20emails.%20%26quot%3BI%20literally%20painted%20a%20picture%20of%20his%20wrecked%20sub%20at%20the%20bottom%2C%20and%20even%20that%20isn't%20enough.%20He%20was%20risking%20his%20life%20and%20his%20customers'%20lives%20to%20go%20down%20in%20history%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%20during%20the%20interview.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20few%20weeks%20ago%2C%20experts