D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESince%20the%20agreement%20had%20to%20be%20renewed%20every%2060%20days%2C%20it%20has%20been%20extended%20three%20times%2C%20with%20the%20most%20recent%20one%20in%20May.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERussia%20had%20withdrawn%20from%20the%20deal%20even%20though%20the%20United%20Nations%20had%20proposed%20to%20President%20Vladimir%20Putin%20that%20they%20would%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.reuters.com%2Fmarkets%2Fcommodities%2Fun-chief-sends-putin-proposal-keep-black-sea-grain-deal-alive-2023-07-12%2F%5C%22%3Erestore%20access%20for%20the%20subsidiary%20of%20a%20Russian%20bank%20to%20the%20SWIFT%3C%2Fa%3E%20international%20payment%20system%20in%20exchange%20for%20an%20extension.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20UN%20Secretary%20General%20had%20said%20that%20the%20lapse%20of%20the%20deal%20which%20facilitated%20the%20export%20of%20more%20than%2030%20million%20tonnes%20of%20Ukrainian%20food%20grains%20%E2%80%9C%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.un.org%2Fen%2Fstory%2F2023%2F07%2F1138752%23%3A~%3Atext%3DUN%2520Secretary%252DGeneral%2520Ant%25C3%25B3nio%2520Guterres%2Chunger%2520and%2520spiralling%2520food%2520costs.%5C%22%3Ewill%20strike%20a%20blow%20to%20people%20in%20need%20everywhere%3C%2Fa%3E%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEarlier%20in%20the%20day%2C%20the%20Ukrainian%20embassy%20in%20India%20had%20issued%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Findia.mfa.gov.ua%2Fen%2Fnews%2Frussia-must-stop-playing-hunger-games-people-around-world%5C%22%3Epress%20note%3C%2Fa%3E%20calling%20on%20all%20%E2%80%9CUN%20Member%20States%20to%20firmly%20demand%20that%20Russia%20resume%20its%20participation%20in%20the%20deal%20and%20stop%20its%20hunger%20games%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmid.ru%2Fen%2Fforeign_policy%2Fnews%2F1897157%2F%5C%22%3ERussian%20foreign%20ministry%E2%80%99s%20announcement%3C%2Fa%3E%20of%20withdrawal%20had%20claimed%20that%20several%20provisions%20of%20the%20Black%20Sea%20grain%20agreement%20had%20no