sraeli-antiquities-74d9e037%3Fmod%3Dhp_lead_pos10%5C%22%3EThe%20Wall%20Street%20Journal.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETrump%20this%20week%20agreed%20to%20return%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fisrael-struggling-artifacts-back-donald-trump-mar-a-lago-report-2023-7%5C%22%3Ea%20collection%20of%20ancient%20Israeli%20artifacts%20that%20have%20been%20%26quot%3Bstuck%26quot%3B%20in%20the%20US%20for%20four%20years%3C%2Fa%3E%20after%20the%20country's%20antiquities%20authorities%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.haaretz.com.%2Fisrael-news%2F2023-07-18%2Fty-article%2F.premium%2Fisraeli-antiquities-remain-stranded-at-trumps-estate-as-authorities-fail-to-retrieve%2F00000189-6448-dc6b-a3f9-ee593e850000%3Futm_source%3Dflipboard%26utm_content%3Dtopic%252Fmiddleeast%5C%22%3Estarted%20publicly%20pushing%20for%20their%20retrieval.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%20data-type%3D%5C%22paragraph%5C%22%3EThe%20Journal%20on%20Thursday%20shed%20new%20light%20on%20the%20long%2C%20strange%20tale%20of%20a%20collection%20of%20ceramic%20oil%20lamps%20that%20traveled%20from%20Israel%20to%20Washington%2C%20DC%2C%20to%20California%2C%20and%20Florida%20over%20the%20course%20of%20four%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%20data-type%3D%5C%22paragraph%5C%22%3EThe%20oil%20lamps'%20US%20journey%20was%20spearheaded%20in%202019%20by%20Saul%20Fox%2C%20a%20private%20equity%20executive%20and%20major%20Jewish-American%20donor%20to%20the%20Israeli%20Antiquities%20Authority%2C%20who%20suggested%20the%20agency%20allow%20the%20items%20to%20be%20presented%20to%20Trump%20at%20a%20forthcoming%20White%20House%20Hanukkah%20party%20to%20thank%20the%20then-president%20for%20his%20support%20of%20Israel%2C%20according%20to%20The%20Journal.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%20data-type%3D%5C%22paragraph%5C%22%3EIsrael%20sent%20the%20national%20treasures%20to%20the%20US%20on%20the%20condition%20that%20the%20valuable%20antiques%20be%20returned%20to%20their%20home%20country%20within%20weeks.%20The%20oil%20lamps%20were%20never%20publicly%20displayed%20at%20the%20White%20House%2C%20however%2C%20due%20to%20a%20State%20Department%20inspection%20into%20the%20items%20that%20ran%20long%2C%20Fox%20told%20The%20Journal.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%20data-type%3D%5C%22paragraph%5C%22%3EWhen%20the%20lamps%20were%20released%20from%20State%20Department%20custody%2C%20Fox%20sent%20a%20courier%20to%20retrieve%20them%20and%20bring%20them%20back%20to%20his%20California%20home%2C%20where%20he%20locked%20them%20up%20and%20%26quot%3Bsort%20of%20forgot%20about%20it%26quot%3B%20right%20as%20the%20pandemic%20hit%20and%20travel%20slowed%20to%20a%20stop%2C%20he%20told%20the%20outlet.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20Fox%20was%20next%20invited%20to%20a%20Trump%20party%20in%20December%202021%2C%20this%20time%20at%20the%20former%20president's%20Mar-a-Lago%20resort%20in%20Florida%2C%20he%20told%20The%20Journal%20that%20he%20made%20a%20plan%20with%20the%20director%20of%20Israeli%20antiquities%20to%20present%20the%20ceramic%20oil%20lamps%20to%20Trump%20two%20years%20later%20than%20originally%20planned.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAlone%20together%20in%20Trump's%20office%20ahead%20of%20the%20holiday%20party%2C%20Fox%20told%20the%20Journal%20that%20he%20was%20preparing%20to%20present%20the%20antiques%20when%20the%20former%20president%20made%20a%20move%20to%20leave.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20stood%20in%20his%20way%20and%20said%2C%20'Mr.%20President%2C%20no%2C%20no%2C%20you%20can't%20leave%2C%20I%20have%20these%20words%20that%20I%20wrote%2C'%26quot%3B%20Fox%20told%20the%20outlet%20he%20said%2C%20starting%20to%20praise%20the%20former%20president%20for%20moving%20the%20US%20Embassy%20to%20Jerusalem.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETrump%2C%20however%2C%20responded%20with%20a%20passionate%20outcry%2C%20according%20to%20Fox%2C%20who%20said%20the%20former%20president%20slammed%20his%20hand%20on%20his%20desk.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWell%2C%20how%20come%20I%20only%20got%2025%25%20of%20the%20Jewish%20vote%3F%26quot%3B%20Fox%20recalled%20Trump%20saying.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPo