20height%3D%5C%221961%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EPresident%20Joe%20Biden%20and%20his%20son%20Hunter%20Biden.%3Cp%3EAP%20Photo%2FManuel%20Balce%20Ceneta%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EGOP%20Sen.%20Chuck%20Grassley%20published%20an%20FBI%20document%20containing%20an%20unverified%20allegation%20made%20by%20a%20Ukrainian%20CEO.%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EThe%20Ukrainian%20executive%20boasted%20he'd%20bribed%20Joe%20and%20Hunter%20Biden%2C%20an%20FBI%20informant%20claimed.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EFBI%20told%20Insider%20the%20release%20of%20the%20document%20%26quot%3Bat%20minimum%20%E2%80%94%20unnecessarily%20risks%20the%20safety%20of%20a%20confidential%20source.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20FBI%20on%20Thursday%20blasted%20two%20top%20Republican%20lawmakers%20for%20supporting%20the%20release%20of%20an%20internal%20investigative%20document%20that%20contains%20unverified%20allegations%20that%20President%20Joe%20Biden%20and%20his%20son%20Hunter%20accepted%20bribes%20from%20a%20Ukrainian%20gas%20company%20%E2%80%94%20claims%20the%20White%20House%20called%20%26quot%3Bdishonest%26quot%3B%20and%20which%20even%20some%20Republicans%20have%20cast%20doubts%20on.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20safeguards%20the%20FBI%20placed%20on%20the%20production%20of%20this%20information%20are%20necessary%20to%20protect%20the%20safety%20of%20confidential%20sources%20and%20the%20integrity%20of%20sensitive%20investigations%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20bureau%20said%20in%20a%20statement%20to%20Insider.%20%26quot%3BToday's%20release%20of%20the%201023%20%5Bform%5D%20-%20at%20a%20minimum%20-%20unnecessarily%20risks%20the%20safety%20of%20a%20confidential%20source.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEarlier%20Thursday%2C%20Sen.%20Chuck%20Grassley%2C%20who%20has%20helped%20lead%20the%20Senate's%20probes%20of%20Hunter%20Biden%2C%20decided%20to%20publish%20a%20sparingly%20redacted%20copy%20of%20the%20FBI%20document%2C%20which%20details%20claims%20made%20by%20a%20confidential%20informant%20who%20said%20a%20Burisma%20executive%20boasted%20about%20how%20he%20used%20Hunter%20Biden%20to%20protect%20the%20company.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20informant%20also%20claimed%20that%20Burisma%20CEO%20Mykola%20Zlochevsky%20claimed%20that%20he%20was%20%26quot%3Bcoerced%26quot%3B%20into%20discussing%20%2410%20million%20bribes%20to%20the%20Bidens%2C%20though%20the%20informant%20was%20unclear%20if%20the%20money%20was%20ever%20paid%20or%20how%3B%20Joe%20Biden%20was%20the%20US%20vice%20president%20at%20the%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20informant%20also%20claimed%2C%20without%20evidence%2C%20that%20Zlochevsky%20made%2017%20recordings%20and%20kept%20documents%20that%20would%20substantiate%20the%20bribery%20allegations.%20Last%20month%2C%20Sen.%20Ron%20Johnson%2C%20who%20has%20teamed%20up%20with%20Grassley%20on%20the%20Biden%20probes%2C%20cautioned%20that%20such%20recordings%20may%20not%20exist.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20could%20be%20coming%20from%20a%20very%20corrupt%20oligarch%20who%20could%20be%20making%20this%20stuff%20up%2C%26quot%3B%20Johnson%20said%20on%20the%20Vicki%20McKenna%20Show%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fpunchbowl.news%2Farchive%2F61523-punchbowl-news-am%2Fcard%2F16%2F%23group-16%5C%22%3Eper%20PunchBowl%20News.%3C%2Fa%3E%20%26quot%3BYou%20have%20to%20suspend%20your%20judgment%20until%20you%20know%20more.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGrassley's%20office%20disputed%20the%20bureau's%20claim%20that%20the%20release%20could%20endanger%20the%20confidential%20informant.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3B%20Democrats%20and%20the%20media%20sought%20to%20link%20the%20FD-1023%20to%20the%20Bidens'%20activity%20in%20Ukraine%20long%20before%20this%20document%20became%20public%2C%20citing%20information%20that%20only%20the%20FBI%20and%20DOJ%20could%20have%20known%2C%26quot%3B%20Grassley%20spokesperson%20Taylor%20Foy%20said%20in%20a%20statement%20to%20Insider.%20%26quot%3BThe%20FBI%20can't%20cite%20risks%20to%20sources%20while%20thwarting%20congressional%20oversight%20in%20one%20breath%20and%20leak%20selective%20information%20to%20the%20news%20media%20in%20another.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20release%20of%20the%20FBI%20document%20come%20days%20after%20former%20President%20Donald%20Trump%2C%20the%202024%20GOP%20frontrunner%2C%20got%20a%20letter%20informing%20him%20that%20he's%20a%20target%20in%20the%20DOJ's%20investigation%20into%20the%20January%206%2C%202021%20Capitol%20riot.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20FBI%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsocxfbi.org%2FSFSA%2FSFSA%2FFeatured-Articles%2FMessage-from-the-FBI-on-the-FD-1023-Request-from-Congress.aspx%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Einitially%20turned%20over%20the%20document%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20Republicans%20in%20June%20in%20response%20to%20a%20subpoena.%20At%20the%20time%2C%20House%20Oversight%20Chairman%20James%20Comer%20had%20pressured%20the%20bureau%20to%20turn%20over%20information%20even%20though%20it%20involved%20a%20confidential%20source.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20FBI%20allowed%20only%20a%20few%20lawmakers%20and%20their%20aides%20access%20to%20the%20document.%20It%20is%20unclear%20how%20Grassley%20obtained%20the%20copy.%20In%20a%20statement%2C%20the%20Iowa%20Republican%20said%20it%20came%20to%20him%20%26quot%3Bvia%20legally%20protected%20disclosures%20by%20Justice%20Department%20whistleblowers.%26quot%3B%20Both%20Grassley%20and%20Comer%20argued%20Thursday%20that%20publicly%20releasing%20the%20document%20was%20a%20necessary%20step.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhile%20the%20FBI%20sought%20to%20obfuscate%20and%20redact%2C%20the%20American%20people%20can%20now%20read%20this%20document%20for%20themselves%2C%20without%20the%20filter%20of%20politicians%20or%20bureaucrats%2C%20thanks%20to%20brave%20and%20heroic%20whistleblowers%2C%26quot%3B%20Grassley%20said%20in%20a%20statement.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERepublicans%20have%20long%20alleged%20that%20when%20he%20was%20vice%20president%2C%20Joe%20Biden%20inappropriately%20meddled%20in%20a%20criminal%20investigation