n%20is%20involved%20with%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fryanmhendrickson.com%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ETip%20of%20the%20Spear%20initiative%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20his%20crowdfunded%20organization%20focused%20on%20removing%20land%20mines%20and%20booby%20traps%20in%20areas%20in%20the%20rear%2C%20areas%20where%20civilians%20are%20most%20at%20risk%20of%20being%20hurt%20or%20killed.%20In%20the%20field%2C%20he%20said%2C%20he%20and%20his%20team%20have%20encountered%20complex%20schemes%20where%20the%20minelayers%20intended%20to%20trap%20and%20maim%20or%20kill%20the%20de-mining%20crews%2C%20which%20are%20out%20in%20it%20working%20primarily%20on%20foot%20using%20man-portable%20mine-clearing%20tools.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221024%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Ukrainian%20army's%2035th%20Marine%20Brigade%20members%20conduct%20mine%20clearance%20work%20at%20a%20field%20in%20Donetsk%2C%20Ukraine%20on%20July%2011%2C%202023.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F64b88b478a4e660019e3c11d%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22649%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EUkrainian%20army's%2035th%20Marine%20Brigade%20members%20conduct%20mine%20clearance%20work%20at%20a%20field%20in%20Donetsk%2C%20Ukraine%20on%20July%2011%2C%202023.%3Cp%3EErcin%20Erturk%2FAnadolu%20Agency%20via%20Getty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EHendrickson%20indicated%20he%20is%20overwhelmed%20by%20the%20number%20of%20mines%20in%20Ukraine%20and%20the%20daunting%20task%20that%20lies%20ahead.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20that%20based%20on%20what%20he%20has%20seen%2C%20it%20is%20plausible%20that%20Ukraine%20will%20not%20ever%20be%20completely%20de-mined.%20%26quot%3BThere's%20too%20many%20land%20mines%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20told%20the%20Ukrainian%20YouTube%20channel.%20And%20there's%20likely%20to%20be%20many%20more%20before%20all%20is%20said%20and%20done.%20As%20they%20are%20effective%20death%20traps%20that%20are%20dan