rs-1235675600%2Famp%2F%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fvariety.com%2F2023%2Ffilm%2Fnews%2Fsamuel-l-jackson-a-time-to-kill-cut-scenes-robbed-me-oscars-1235675600%2Famp%2F%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%2216%20killed%2C%20100%20missing%20as%20landslide%20buries%20hamlet%20in%20Maharashtra%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1689888286000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-101996251%2Cimgsize-130062.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fcity%2Fmumbai%2F16-killed-100-missing-as-rain-triggered-landslide-buries-hamlet-in-maharashtra%2Farticleshow%2F101996231.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22In%20one%20of%20the%20biggest%20natural%20disasters%20in%20Maharashtra%2C%20a%20massive%20landslide%20precipitated%20by%20over%20400mm%20of%20rainfall%20flattened%20a%20remote%20tribal%20hamlet%20named%20Irshalwadi%20in%20Khalapur%20tehsil%20in%20the%20foothills%20of%20the%20Sahyadri%20range%20in%20Raigad%20district%20on%20Wednesday%20night.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22UMESH%20K%20PARIDA%2C%20PRIYANKA%20KAKODKAR%2C%20CHITTARANJAN%20TEMBHEKAR%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A1%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fcity%2Fmumbai%2F16-killed-100-missing-as-rain-triggered-landslide-buries-hamlet-in-maharashtra%2Farticleshow%2F101996231.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22It's%20not%20just%20JD%20Vance%3A%20Republican%20senators%20are%20open%20to%20criminalizing%20gender-affirming%20care%20for%20minors%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Sen.%20JD%20Vance%20of%20Ohio%20at%20the%20Capitol%20on%20May%2011%2C%202023.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F64b97f074182d800196a51d1%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221000%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ESen.%20JD%20Vance%20of%20Ohio%20at%20the%20Capitol%20on%20May%2011%2C%202023.%3Cp%3ETom%20Williams%2FCQ-Roll%20Call%20via%20Getty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3ESen.%20JD%20Vance%20introduced%20a%20bill%20to%20criminalize%20providing%20certain%20treatments%20to%20transgender%20minors.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EHe%20has%20defended%20the%20sweeping%20bill%2C%20saying%20it's%20a%20%26quot%3Blong%20way%20from%20becoming%20law.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EOther%20Republican%20senators%20told%20Insider%20that%20they're%20open%20to%20the%20idea%20as%20well.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3ESen.%20JD%20Vance%20on%20Tuesday%20introduced%20a%20sweeping%20bill%20that%20would%20make%20it%20a%20federal%20crime%20to%20provide%20certain%20medical%20treatments%20to%20transgender%20people%20under%20the%20age%20of%2018.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20think%20the%20more%20that%20we%20learn%20about%20so-called%20'gender%20affirming%20care%2C'%20the%20more%20that%20we%20learn%20that%20the%20medical%20science%20is%20being%20way%20outpaced%20by%20the%20way%20that%20patients%20are%20actually%20being%20treated%2C%26quot%3B%20Vance%20told%20Insider%20at%20the%20Capitol%20on%20Thursday.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20Vance%20isn't%20merely%20advocating%20for%20greater%20caution%20and%20study%20of%20the%20procedures%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.wsj.com%2Farticles%2Fu-s-becomes-transgender-care-outlier-as-more-in-europe-urge-caution-6c70b5e0%5C%22%3Elike%20some%20European%20countries%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%94%20his%20legislation%20would%20go%20much%20further%2C%20and%20would%20notably%20make%20it%20harder%20for%20transgender%20adults%20to%20receive%20gender-affirming%20care%20as%20well.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EUnder%20the%20Ohio%20Republican's%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.vance.senate.gov%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2FProtect-Childrens-Innocence-Act.pdf%5C%22%3E%26quot%3BProtect%20Children's%20Innocence%20Act%26quot%3B%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%94%20the%20Senate%20version%20of%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.congress.gov%2Fbill%2F118th-congress%2Fhouse-bill%2F1399%2Ftext%5C%22%3Ebill%20first%20introduced%20last%20year%20by%20Rep.%20Marjorie%20Taylor%20Greene%20of%20Georgia%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%94%20doctors%20would%20face%20up%20to%2012%20years%20in%20prison%20for%20performing%20surgeries%20or%20puberty-blocking%20hormones%20for%20the%20purpose%20of%20a%20gender%20transition.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20also%20aims%20to%20block%20the%20use%20of%20taxpayer%20funds%20for%20gender-affirming%20care%20%E2%80%94%20which%20means%20preventing%20federally-operated%20facilities%20from%20performing%20procedures%2C%20and%20blocking%20several%20health%20plans%20that%20receive%20federal%20funds%20from%20covering%20the%20costs%20of%20gender-affirming%20care.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%20it%20would%20forbid%20institutions%20of%20higher%20education%20from%20offering%20any%20instruction%20on%20such%20procedures%2C%20foreclosing%20the%20ability%20for%20more%20doctors%20to%20receive%20the%20training%20necessary%20to%20perform%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAsked%20about%20potentially%20harmful%20effects%20on%20transgender%20people%20who%20are%20already%20receiving%20care%2C%20Vance%20conceded%20that%20the%20bill%20is%20largely%20a%20messaging%20device%20for%20now.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20bill%20is%20a%20very%20long%20way%20from%20becoming%20law%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Vance.%20%26quot%3BWe%20would%20do%20a%20lot%20to%20figure%20out%20how%20it%20would%20affect%20people%2C%20and%20when%20it%20would%20apply.%20This%20is%20not%20the%20sort%20of%20thing%20that's%20going%20to%20go%20into%20effect%20tomorrow.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%20he%20disputed%20the%20notion%20that%20adults%20would%20be%20significantly%20affected%20by%20the%20bill.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BLook%2C%20I%20think%20certainly%20the%20goal%20is%20to%20prevent%20taxpayer%20funding%20of%20this%20stuff%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Vance.%20%26quot%3BBut%20it%20doesn't%20have%20any%20effect%20on%20the%20capacity%20of%20people%20to%20receive%20this%20care%20if%20they're%20adults.%20The%20goal%20is%20not%20to%20touch%20consenting%20adults.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EThe%20nationalization%20of%20a%20state-level%20trend%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20bill's%20arrival%20in%20the%20Senate%20signals%20the%20nationalization%20of%20a%20conservative%20backlash%20that's%20picked%20up%20steam%20at%20the%20state%20level%20in%20recent%20years%2C%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.semafor.com%2Farticle%2F07%2F20%2F2023%2Fthe-gops-state-fights-over-lgbtq-issues-have-moved-to-congress%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eas%20Semafor's%20Joseph%20Zeballos-Roig%20reported%20this%20week%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETwenty%20states%2C%20mostly%20those%20controlled%20by%20Republicans%2C%20have%20passed%20laws%20or%20enacted%20policies%20banning%20gender-affirming%20care%20for%20individuals%20under%2018%2C%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hrc.org%2Fresources%2Fattacks-on-gender-affirming-care-by-state-map%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eaccording%20to%20the%20Human%20Rights%20Campaign%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20affecting%20more%20than%2030%25%20of%20transgender%20youth.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20bill%20has%20the%20support%20of%2046%20mostly%20hard-right%20House%20Republicans%2C%20Vance%20just%20has%20one%20official%20co-sponsor%20in%20the%20Senate%3A%20Sen.%20Tommy%20Tuberville%20of%20Alabama.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20that%20doesn't%20mean%20that%20other%20Republicans%20aren't%20open%20to%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20shouldn't%20be%20doing%20this%20to%20children%20in%20America%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Sen.%20Marco%20Rubio%20of%20Florida%2C%20who%20stressed%20that%20he%20had%20yet%20to%20study%20the%20specifics%20of%20Vance's%20bill.%20%26quot%3BOnce%20people%20turn%2018%2C%20obviously%2C%20those%20options%20are%20in%20the%20domain.%20I%20mean%2C%20I%20don't%20want%20taxpayers%20to%20pay%20for%20those%20options.%20But%20whether%20they%20agree%20with%20it%20or%20not%2C%20we're%20a%20free%20country.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI