igated.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BTroopers%20give%20migrants%20water%2C%26quot%3B%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Ftravisconsidine%2Fstatus%2F1681145494616064000%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EConsidine%20said%20on%20Twitter%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20there%20are%20women%20and%20children%20who%20are%20asking%20for%20water%2C%20they're%20getting%20water%2C%26quot%3B%20Considine%20told%20The%20Times.%20%26quot%3BA%20group%20of%2030%20adult%20males%20comes%2C%20and%20they're%20begging%20for%20water.%20I'm%20not%20going%20to%20say%20there%20are%20not%20troopers%20saying%2C%20'We're%20not%20going%20to%20give%20you%20water.'%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20The%20Times%2C%20Considine%20added%20that%20troopers%20might%20tell%20migrants%20to%20get%20water%20in%20Mexico%20if%20they%20do%20not%20appear%20to%20be%20in%20distress.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAbbott%20also%20released%20a%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fgov.texas.gov%2Fnews%2Fpost%2Foperation-lone-star-statement-on-orders-addressing-illegal-crossings%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%C2%A0statement%3C%2Fa%3E%20Tuesday%20saying%20that%20%26quot%3Bno%20orders%20or%20directions%20have%20been%20given%20under%20Operation%20Lone%20Star%20that%20would%20compromise%20the%20lives%20of%20those%20attempting%20to%20cross%20the%20border%20illegally.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAbbott's%20office%20did%20not%20respond%20to%20an%20inquiry%20to%20address%20the%20specific%20accounts%20from%20Wingate.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20details%20in%20the%20email%20provide%20a%20glimpse%20of%20some%20of%20the%20risks%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.texastribune.org%2F2023%2F05%2F15%2Ftexas-border-migrant-encounters-title-42-drop%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ethousands%20of%20migrants%3C%2Fa%3E%20attempting%20to%20cross%20the%20US-Mexico%20border%20each%20day%20face.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWingate%20claimed%20in%20an%20email%20to%20have%20witnessed%20a%20pregnant%20woman%20who%20was%20having%20a%20miscarriage%20getting%20caught%20in%20the%20wire.%20In%20another%20account%2C%20a%20four-year-old%20girl%20passed%20out%20from%20heat%20exhaustion%20and%20was%20pushed%20back%20by%20National%20Guard%20soldiers%2C%20the%20Chronicle%20reported.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20trooper%20also%20sent%20an%20email%20to%20a%20superior%20that%20suggested%20razor%20wire-wrapped%20barrels%20were%20installed%20in%20some%20parts%20of%20the%20river%20%E2%80%94%20describing%20them%20as%20%26quot%3Btraps%26quot%3B%20%E2%80%94%20that%20can%20increase%20the%20risk%20of%20drowning%20because%20they%20push%20people%20into%20deeper%20parts%20of%20the%20river%2C%20according%20to%20the%20report.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EConsidine%20told%20The%20Times%20that%20%26quot%3Bbarrel%20traps%26quot%3B%20were%20not%20deployed%20but%20that%20it%20was%20possible%20a%20barrel%20wrapped%20in%20razor%20wire%20floated%20away.%20His%20department%20has%20yet%20to%20confirm%20the%20case%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20believe%20we%20a%20have%20stepped%20over%20a%20line%20into%20the%20in%20humane%2C%26quot%3B%20Wingate%C2%A0wrote%2C%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.breitbart.com%2Fborder%2F2023%2F07%2F18%2Ftexas-investigates-allegations-of-inhumane-border-policies-made-by-state-trooper%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eaccording%20to%20Breitbart%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20which%20revealed%20more%20aspects%20of%20the%20trooper's%20email.%20%26quot%3BWe%20need%20to%20operate%20it%20correctly%20in%20the%20eyes%20of%20God.%20We%20need%20to%20recognize%20that%20these%20are%20people%20who%20are%20made%20in%20the%20image%20of%20God%20and%20need%20to%20be%20treated%20as%20such.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftexas-trooper-calls-gov-abbotts-border-security-inhumane-reports-2023-7%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%