%20the%20NIA%2C%20Faizan%20hatched%20a%20criminal%20conspiracy%20along%20with%20his%20associates%20and%20other%20unknown%20individuals%20through%20social%20media%20platforms%20to%20support%20ISIS%20activities%20in%20India%20and%20disseminate%20the%20outfit's%20propaganda%20on%20social%20media.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20conspiracy%20was%20aimed%20at%20carrying%20out%20violent%20terror%20attacks%20in%20India%20on%20behalf%20of%20the%20ISIS%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20NIA%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EInvestigations%20revealed%20that%20Faizan%20and%20his%20associates%20had%20pledged%20their%20allegiance%20to%20the%20ISIS%2C%20the%20agency%20said%2C%20adding%2C%20%26quot%3BThe%20accused%20was%20also%20actively%20in%20the%20process%20of%20radicalizing%20neo-converts%20and%20attracting%20them%20to%20the%20terrorist%20fold%20for%20enriching%20the%20cadre%20base%20of%20the%20ISIS%20in%20India.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFaizan%20was%20in%20contact%20with%20ISIS%20handlers%20based%20outside%20India%2C%20who%20were%20guiding%20him%20on%20recruitment%20to%20the%20outfit%2C%20the%20NIA%20claimed.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAlong%20with%20other%20ISIS%20members%2C%20he%20was%20planning%20violent%20actions%20and%20was%20contemplating%20doing%20'hijrat'%20to%20an%20ISIS%20conflict%20theatre%20abroad%2C%26quot%3B%20it%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1689878400000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2018-12%2F9cmll0r_nia-generic-650_625x300_27_December_18.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Faligarh-muslim-university-student-arrested-over-alleged-isis-links-4226698%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20National%20Investigation%20Agency%20(NIA)%20on%20Thursday%20arrested%20a%2019-year-old%20student%20of%20Uttar%20Pradesh's%20Aligarh%20Muslim%20University%20(AMU)%20over%20his%20alleged%20links%20with%20terrorist%20organisation%20ISIS.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A3%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2