3Cp%3EThe%20complainants%20had%20spoken%20to%20the%20survivors%20and%20then%20emailed%20NCW%20chairperson%20Rekha%20Sharma.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3ENewslaundry%3C%2Fem%3E%C2%A0accessed%20a%20copy%20of%20the%20complaint.%20It%20was%20emailed%20to%20chairperson-ncw%40nic.in%2C%20complaintcell-ncw%40nic.in%20and%20northeastcell-ncw%40nic.in.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20complaint%20clearly%20stated%20that%20on%20May%204%2C%20two%20women%20from%20a%20village%20in%20Kangpokpi%20district%20were%20%E2%80%9Cdisrobed%2C%20paraded%20naked%2C%20beaten%20and%20then%20encircled%20by%20a%20marauding%20Meitei%20mob%20and%20raped%20in%20public%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fleaders-express-outrage-over-brutality-impunity-with-which-women-were-assaulted-in-manipur-violence%5C%22%3ELeaders%20Outraged%20Over%20the%20Brutality%20and%20the%20Impunity%20With%20Which%20Women%20Were%20Assaulted%20in%20Manipur%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20letter%20made%20an%20urgent%20appeal%20to%20the%20NCW%20to%20%E2%80%9Curgently%20assess%20the%20disproportionate%20victimization%20of%20Kuki-Zomi%20indigenous%20tribal%20women%20through%20brutal%20and%20inhumane%20acts%20of%20sexual%20violence%2C%20including%20rape%2C%20kidnapping%2C%20public%20lynching%2C%20immolation%20and%20murder%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWitness%20accounts%20reveal%20the%20most%20harrowing%20and%20distressing%20details%2C%20including%20the%20incrimination%20of%20Meitei%20women%20vigilantes%20as%20enablers%20and%20perpetrators%20of%20gender-based%20violence.%20Victims%20and%20survivors%20allege%20that%20Meitei%20women%20vigilantes%20have%20actively%20participated%20in%20the%20attacks%20and%20assaults%20on%20Kuki-Zomi%20women%20and%20children%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20complaint%20alleged.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CSeveral%20Kuki-Zomi%20women%20have%20been%20forced%20to%20flee%20for%20their%20lives%20during%20advanced%20stages%2