monstration%20at%20the%20Manipur%20Bhawan%20in%20the%20national%20capital%20to%20protest%20against%20the%20sexual%20violence%20and%20forcible%20stripping%20and%20parading%20of%20the%20women.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20assault%20took%20place%20three%20months%20ago%2C%20the%20video%20went%20viral%20only%20on%20Thursday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIn%20a%20very%20disturbing%20manner%2C%20mobile%20recorded%20videos%20have%20surfaced%20on%20social%20media%20where%20a%20group%20of%20men%20have%20been%20seen%20parading%20two%20women%20naked%20on%20the%20streets.%20It%20is%20very%20shocking%20that%20these%20videos%20were%20not%20only%20recorded%20but%20also%20posted%20on%20digital%20platforms%20revealing%20the%20identity%20of%20these%20women.%20It%20violates%20the%20dignity%20and%20rights%20of%20the%20survivors%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20women%20leaders%20said%20in%20the%20statement.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20fact%20that%20this%20incident%20had%20happened%20on%20May%204%2C%20right%20after%20the%20ethnic%20violence%20began%20on%203%20May%20this%20year%2C%20and%20no%20action%20was%20taken%20more%20than%20a%20mere%20zero%20FIR%2C%20makes%20the%20police%20apathy%20with%20the%20victims%20and%20collusion%20with%20the%20perpetrators%20of%20the%20crime%20abundantly%20clear.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20leaders%20also%20condemned%20the%20%E2%80%9Ccomplete%20silence%E2%80%9D%20of%20Manipur%20chief%20minister%20Biren%20Singh%20and%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20on%20the%20ongoing%20unrest%20in%20the%20northeastern%20region.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAdded%20to%20this%20is%20the%20deafening%20silence%20of%20the%20CM%20and%20PM%20which%20is%20highly%20condemnable.%20Women%20have%20become%20the%20direct%20victims%20of%20the%20ongoing%20ethnic%20violence%20in%20the%20state%2C%E2%80%9D%20read%20the%20statement.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20more%20than%2070%20days%20of%20violence%20in%20Manipur%2C%20which%20led%20to%20loss%20of%20about%20150%20lives%20and%20left%20tens%20of%20thousands%20displaced%2C%20Prime%20Minister%20Modi%20spoke%20on%20the%20situation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20his%20address%2C%20he%20said%20that%20%E2%80%9Call%20states%E2%80%9D%20must%20do%20whatever%20they%20can%20to%20protect%20%E2%80%9Cour%20mothers%20and%20sisters%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fnarendra-modi-talked-about-the-manipur-violence-but-did-he-really%5C%22%3Eanalysed%3C%2Fa%3E%20how%20the%20prime%20minister%20picked%20on%20this%20one%20incident%2C%20seemingly%20forgetting%20the%20context%20it%20had%20occurred%20in.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20leaders%20have%20demanded%20immediate%20arrest%20of%20the%20accused%20and%20fast-tracking%20of%20the%20case%3B%20action%20against%20the%20policemen%20responsible%20for%20dereliction%20of%20duty%3B%20and%20resignation%20of%20chief%20minister%20Biren%20Singh.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThey%20have%20also%20asked%20the%20authorities%20to%20take%20immediate%20steps%20to%20restore%20peace%20in%20Manipur.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20women%20leaders%20who%20addressed%20the%20gathering%20were%20Mariam%20Dhawale%20(AIDWA)%2C%20Deepti%20Bharti%20(NFIW)%2C%20Poonam%20Kaushik%20(Pragatisheel%20MS)%2C%20Ritu%20Kaushik%20(AIMSS)%2C%20Nobita%20(CSW)%2C%20Lambi%20(NEFIS)%2C%20Kusum%20Sehgal%20and%20(Zimmedari%20SWO).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESeparately%2C%20the%20Mahila%20Congress%20and%20the%20Indian%20Youth%20Congress%20(IYC)%20on%20Thursday%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nationalheraldindia.com%2Fnational%2Fmahila-congress-youth-congress-protestors-demand-manipur-cm-biren-singhs-removal%5C%22%3E%20staged%20a%20protest%3C%2Fa%3E%20over%20the%20incident%20and%20demanded%20resignation%20of%20Biren%20Singh.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESpeaking%20to%20the%20media%2C%20Mahila%20Congress%20acting%20president%20Netta%20D%E2%80%99Souza%20said%20that%20the%20chief%20minister%20has%20failed%20in%20controlling%20the%20law%20and%20order%20situat