20wholly%20milled%20rice%2C%20whether%20or%20not%20polished%20or%20glazed.%20However%2C%20there%20has%20been%20no%20change%20in%20the%20export%20policy%20of%20non-basmati%20rice%20(par%20boiled%20rice)%20and%20basmati%20rice%2C%20which%20forms%20the%20bulk%20of%20rice%20exports.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20Directorate%20General%20of%20Foreign%20Trade%2C%20the%20government%20amended%20the%20export%20policy%20of%20the%20commodity%20from%20%E2%80%9Cfree%E2%80%9D%20to%20%E2%80%9Cprohibited%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIn%20order%20to%20ensure%20adequate%20availability%20of%20non-basmati%20white%20rice%20in%20the%20Indian%20market%20and%20to%20allay%20the%20rise%20in%20prices%20in%20the%20domestic%20market%2C%20Government%20of%20India%20has%20amended%20the%20Export%20Policy%20of%20the%20above%20variety%20from%20%E2%80%98Free%20with%20export%20duty%20of%2020%25%E2%80%99%20to%20%E2%80%98Prohibited%E2%80%99%20with%20immediate%20effect%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20the%20Ministry%20of%20Consumer%20Affairs%2C%20Food%20and%20Public%20Distribution.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CDomestic%20prices%20of%20rice%20are%20on%20an%20increasing%20trend.%20Retail%20prices%20have%20increased%20by%2011.5%25%20over%20a%20year%20and%203%25%20over%20the%20past%20month%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20ministry%20said%20in%20a%20statement.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENon-basmati%20white%20rice%20constitutes%20about%2025%25%20of%20the%20total%20rice%20exported%20from%20the%20country.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20prohibition%20on%20export%20of%20non-basmati%20white%20rice%20will%20lead%20to%20lowering%20of%20prices%20for%20the%20consumers%20in%20the%20country%2C%E2%80%9D%20it%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThe%20Economic%20Times%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Feconomictimes.indiatimes.com%2Fnews%2Feconomy%2Fagriculture%2Fgovt-bans-export-of-non-basmati-white-rice%2Farticleshow%2F101989078.cms%3Ffrom%3Dmdr%5C%22%3Ehad%20reported%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20uneven%20distribution%20of%20rainfall%20in%20the%20key%20rice-growing%20areas%20of%20the%20country%20pushed%20up%20prices%20of%20the%20grain%20by%20up%20to%2020%25%20in%20the%20last%20ten%20days.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20move%20also%20comes%20a%20month%20after%20the%20Union%20government%20disallowed%20the%20Food%20Corporation%20of%20India%20(FCI)%20to%20sell%20rice%20directly%20to%20states%2C%20including%20Karnataka%2C%20which%20had%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Funion-govt-trying-to-scuttle-karnatakas-free-rice-scheme-by-changing-rules-for-fci-siddaramaiah%5C%22%3Ehad%20reached%3C%2Fa%3E%20a%20deal%20with%20the%20FCI%20to%20buy%202.28%20lakh%20metric%20tons%20of%20rice%20at%20Rs%203%2C400%20per%20quintal.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20state%20made%20the%20agreement%20with%20the%20Corporation%20for%20its%20Anna%20Bhagya%20programme%2C%20which%20was%20part%20of%20its%20election%20promises.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20day%20after%20Karnataka%E2%80%99s%20agreement%20with%20the%20FCI%2C%20the%20Union%20government%20directed%20the%20Corporation%20to%20release%2015%20lakh%20metric%20tonnes%20of%20rice%20and%20wheat%20in%20the%20open%20market%20and%20stop%20direct%20sale%20to%20states%2C%20except%20those%20in%20the%20north%20east.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1689869405000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F04%2F03164309%2FDSC2224-1024x684-1.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fgovt-bans-exports-of-non-basmati-white-rice-with-immediate-effect%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Non-basmati%20white%20rice%20constitutes%20about%2025%25%20of%20the%20total%20rice%20exported%20from%20the%20country.%20The%20prohibition%20on%20export%20of%20non-basmati%20white%20rice%20will%20lead%20to%20lowering%20of%20prices%20for%20the%20consumers%20in%20the%20country%2C%20said%20the%20government.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fgovt-bans-exports-of-non-basmati-white-