ices%20B.R.%20Gavai%2C%20J.B.%20Pardiwala%20and%20Prashant%20Kumar%20Mishra%20took%20cognizance%20of%20the%20recent%20cheetah%20deaths%20that%20the%20project%20%E2%80%93%20which%20aims%20to%20introduce%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%20African%20cheetahs%20in%20India%E2%80%99s%20grasslands%20%E2%80%93%20%3C%2Fspan%3Ehas%20witnessed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CTwo%20more%20deaths%20last%20week.%20Why%20is%20this%20becoming%20a%20prestige%20issue%3F%20Please%20take%20some%20positive%20steps%2C%E2%80%9D%20Justice%20B.R.%20Gavai%20said%2C%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.barandbench.com%2Fnews%2Flitigation%2Fcheetah-deaths-kuno-supreme-court-shift-rajasthan%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Eaccording%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20to%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EBar%20and%20Bench%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOf%20the%2020%20animals%20that%20were%20brought%20to%20Kuno%20from%20Namibia%20and%20South%20Africa%2C%20five%20have%20died%20so%20far.%20Three%20cubs%2C%20born%20in%20India%2C%20have%20also%20died.%20The%20last%20two%20deaths%20occurred%20last%20week%2C%20on%20July%2011%20and%2014.%20Experts%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fenvironment%2Fproject-cheetah-deaths-radio-collar-infections%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Ehave%20said%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20that%20the%20septicaemia%20that%20the%20animals%20died%20of%20was%20caused%20by%20the%20accumulation%20of%20moisture%20under%20the%20animals%E2%80%99%20radio%20collars%20(gadgets%20fitted%20on%20their%20necks%2C%20that%20help%20track%20and%20monitor%20their%20movement)%2C%20which%20gave%20rise%20to%20wounds%20that%20subsequently%20got%20infected.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CWhat%20is%20the%20problem%20exactly%3F%E2%80%9D%20asked%20Justice%20Pardiwala%2C%20regarding%20the%20recent%20cheetah%20deaths.%20%E2%80%9CPrima%20facie%20it%20appears%20that%20our%20conditions%20don%E2%80%99t%20suit%20them.%E2%80%9D%20Justice%20Gavai%20also%20said%20that%20%E2%80%9C40%25%20deaths%20occurring%20in%20less%20than%20a%20year%20does%20not%20paint%20a%20good%20picture%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20response%20to%20the%20bench%E2%80%99s%20queries%2C%20the%20Union%20government%20responded%20that%20up%20to%2050%25%20of%20deaths%20in%20the%20first%20year%20of%20the%20programme%20is%20%E2%80%9Canticipated%E2%80%9D.%20A%20%E2%80%9Cdetailed%20analysis%E2%80%9D%20of%20each%20death%20is%20being%20done%20and%20will%20be%20included%20in%20the%20status%20report%20that%20will%20be%20submitted%20to%20the%20court%2C%20it%20said.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20Read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fenvironment%2Fthree-more-cheetahs-in-kuno-have-neck-infections%5C%22%3EThree%20More%20Cheetahs%20Have%20Neck%20Infections%3B%20Expert%20Says%20Last%20Cheetah%20Death%20%E2%80%98Potentially%20Avoidable%E2%80%99%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EConsider%20sites%20in%20Rajasthan%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EJustice%20Gavai%20also%20asked%20why%20the%20animals%20were%20all%20put%20in%20one%20place%20instead%20of%20being%20spread%20out.%20The%20Supreme%20Court%20had%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.livelaw.in%2Ftop-stories%2Fsupreme-court-cheetah-kuno-reintroduction-alternative-habitats-concerns-229029%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Ealready%20asked%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20the%20Union%20government%20to%20look%20at%20%E2%80%9Calternate%20sites%E2%80%9D%20%E2%80%93%20either%20in%20Madhya%20Pradesh%20or%20Rajasthan%20%E2%80%93%20for%20the%20cheetah%20introduction%20in%20May%20this%20year.%20A%20bench%20of%20Justices%20Gavai%20and%20Sanjay%20Karol%20had%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Findianexpress.com%2Farticle%2Findia%2Fsc-concerned-death-cheetahs-knp-centre-consider-shifting-rajasthan-8617113%2F%23%3A~%3Atext%3DStating%2520that%2520there%2520is%2520%25E2%2580%259Ctoo%2Cin%2520Madhya%2520Pradesh%2520or%2520Rajasthan%25E2%2580%259D.%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Eremarked%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20then%20that%20Kuno%20is%20%E2%80%9Cnot%20sufficient%20to%20accommodate%E2%80%9D%20the%20cheetahs%20and%20that%20there%20was%20%E2%80%9Ctoo%20much%20concentration%20of%20cheetahs%20at%20one%20place%E2%80%9D.%20The%20court%20had%20also%20said%20that%20%E2%80%9Cparty-politics%E2%80%9D%20should%20not%20be%20part%20of%20the%20issue%2C%20and%20that%20just%20because%20Rajasthan%20is%20ruled%20by%20the%20Congress%2C%20it%20does%20not%20mean%20shifting%20the%20cheetahs%20there%20cannot%20be%20considered%2C%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fscroll.in%2Flatest%2F1049396%2Fconsider-shifting-cheetahs-to-alternate-locations-sc-asks-centre%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Ereported%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EPTI%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EBar%20and%20Bench%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%20%3Cspan%3Ereported%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%20that%20on%20July%2020%2C%20Justice%20Gavai%20%E2%80%9Corally%20suggested%E2%80%9D%20that%20some%20of%20the%20cheetahs%20be%20shifted%20to%20Rajasthan.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9COne%20of%20the%20sanctuaries%20in%20Rajasthan%20(Jawai%20National%20Park)%20is%20very%20famous%20for%20leopards.%20200%20kilometres%20from%20Udaipur%2C%20I%20believe.%20Sighting%20is%20very%20good%20there.%20Have%20one%20more%20sanctuary%20there%20for%20cheetahs%2C%20consider%20it%20as%20a%20positive%20bias%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20is%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3Ereported%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%20to%20have%20said.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHowever%2C%20the%20Union%20government%20said%20that%20there%20are%20problems%20in%20making%20arrangements%20in%20other%20states%2C%20and%20it%20was%20%E2%80%9Cnot%20about%20politics%E2%80%9D.%20A%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Ci%3EHindustan%20Times%20%3C%2Fi%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hindustantimes.com%2Findia-news%2Fsupreme-court-seeks-government-response-on-eight-cheetah-deaths-expresses-concern-over-project-cheetah-s-progress-101689839888526.html%5C%22%3Ereport%20said%20that%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%C2%A0the%20government%20added%20that%20six%20tigers%20had%20died%20after%20relocation%20to%20a%20national%20park%20in%20Rajasthan.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20next%20hearing%20has%20been%20posted%20for%20August%201.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Supreme%20Court%20appointed%20a%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwii.gov.in%2Fimages%2Fimages%2Fdocuments%2Fpublications%2Faction_plan_cheetah_introduction_jan_2022.pdf%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Ethree-member%20expert%20committee%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20in%202020%20to%20guide%20the%20National%20Tiger%20Conservation%20Authority%20(NTCA)%20in%20the%20cheetah%20introduction.%20Its%20members%20are%20conservationist%20and%20former%20IAS%20officer%20M.K.%20Ranjitsinh%2C%20Dhananjai%20Mohan%20(currently%20the%20director%20of%20the%20Wildlife%20Institute%20of%20India)%20and%20the%20additional%20director%20general%20(wildlife)%2C%20Ministry%20of%20Environment%2C%20Forest%20and%20Climate%20Change.%20As%20per%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Findianexpress.com%2Farticle%2Findia%2Fday-after-namibian-cheetah-dies-sc-seeks-task-force-experts-qualification-experience-8524229%2F%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Ereports%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20the%20Union%20government%20said%20in%20March%20this%20year%20that%20since%20the%20cheetahs%20have%20been%20introduced%20in%20India%2C%20it%20was%20no%20longer%20necessary%20for%20the%20NTCA%20to%20continue%20to%20take%20the%20guidance%20and%20advice%20of%20the%20expert%20committee.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ENow%2C%20the%20expert%20committee%20in%20their%20plea%20to%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20have%20urged%20it%20to%20direct%20the%20NTCA%20to%20keep%20it%20updated%20on%20the%20latest%20developments%2C%20and%20accept%20their%20advi