3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAnant%20Vijay%2C%20a%20senior%20journalist%20with%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EDainik%20Jagran%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20and%20author%20of%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EDynasty%20to%20Democracy%3A%20The%20Untold%20Story%20of%20Smriti%20Irani%E2%80%99s%20Triumph%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20in%20his%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22http%3A%2F%2Fhaahaakar.blogspot.com%2F2023%2F07%2Fblog-post_13.html%5C%22%3Ecolumn%20on%20July%2016%3C%2Fa%3E%20wrote%20that%20the%20January%201948%20issue%20of%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EKalyan%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20(%E2%80%98%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3ENari%20Ank%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%99)%20was%20ready%20when%20the%20news%20of%20assassination%20of%20Gandhi%20by%20Nathuram%20Godse%2C%20a%20member%20of%20the%20RSS%2C%20came.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3ENari%20Ank%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20had%20already%20been%20dispatched%2C%20but%20in%20the%20few%20issues%20that%20were%20still%20left%2C%20three%20pages%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%C2%A0mourning%20Gandhi%E2%80%99s%20killing%20were%20attached.%20Anant%20reproduces%20those%20pages.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3ENari%20Ank%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20remains%20one%20of%20the%20most%20popular%20annual%20issues%20of%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EKalyan%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3Ewhich%20has%20been%20in%20constant%20reprint%20since%201948.%20Ideally%2C%20those%20three%20pages%20should%20have%20been%20part%20of%20subsequent%20reprints.%20I%20consulted%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3ENari%20Ank%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20reprinted%20in%202002%20which%20has%20no%20mention%20of%20Gandhi%E2%80%99s%20killing.%20Also%20missing%20are%20those%20three%20pages%20which%20the%20likes%20of%20Anant%20are%20tom-toming%20as%20a%20proof%20of%20Gita%20Press%E2%80%99s%20deep%20love%20for%20Gandhi.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAnant%20cooks%20up%20a%20bizarre%20reason%20for%20the%20absence%20of%20these%20pages%20from%20later%20editions.%20He%20says%20it%20is%20%E2%80%98%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3Esamanya%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%20%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3Eprakriya%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%99%20(common%20practice)%20of%20the%20publishing%20industry%20to%20leave%20out%20references%20to%20contemporary%20events.%20If%20anything%2C%20it%20is%20not%20%E2%80%98%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3Esamanya%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%99%2C%20but%20the%20most%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3Easamanya%20prakriya%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20(uncommon%20practice)%20and%20never%20happens%20in%20the%20publishing%20industry.%20As%20a%20published%20author%2C%20he%20should%20know%2C%20but%20then%2C%20bhakti%20has%20its%20limitations.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EI%20would%20like%20to%20challenge%20Anant%20to%20show%20me%20one%20issue%20of%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EKalyan%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20which%20has%20left%20out%20certain%20things%20since%20they%20are%20no%20longer%20relevant.%20Have%20the%20reprints%20of%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EHindu%20Sankriti%20Ank%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20(January%201950)%2C%20a%20very%20popular%20number%20of%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EKalyan%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20stopped%20referring%20to%20the%20death%20of%20RSS%20founder%20Keshav%20Baliram%20Hedgewar%3F%20No%2C%20it%20has%20not.%20Then%20why%20leave%20out%20Gandhi%20from%20later%20editions%20of%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3ENari%20Ank%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%3F%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIt%20proves%20what%20I%20maintain%20throughout%20my%20book%3B%20Hanuman%20Prasad%20Poddar%20(%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EKalyan%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%99s%20editor)%20and%20Gita%20Press%20had%20an%20intimate%20relationship%20with%20Gandhi%20that%20went%20sour%20on%20ideological%20grounds.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20Read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fhistory%2Fmahatma-gandhi-gita-press%5C%22%3EAfter%20Gandhi%E2%80%99s%20Assassination%2C%20Why%20No%20Mention%20of%20Him%20in%20February%2C%20March%201948%20Issues%20of%20Kalyan%3F%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAlso%2C%20Gita%20Press%20was%20not%20only%20about%20%3Cem%3Ebhakti%3C%2Fem%3E%20(devotion)%2C%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3Egyan%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20(knowledge)%20and%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3Evairagya%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20(renunciation)%2C%20but%20it%20was%20a%20crucial%20cog%20in%20the%20wheel%20of%20Hindu%20nationalism.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIf%20Gita%20Press%20was%20so%20much%20in%20love%20with%20Gandhi%2C%20it%20should%20have%20devoted%20an%20entire%20issue%20to%20him%2C%20just%20as%20it%20did%20for%20Madan%20Mohan%20Malaviya%20in%201946.%20Gita%20Press%20is%20opposed%20to%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3Evyakti%20puja%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20(individual%20worship)%2C%20but%20the%20only%20time%20it%20made%20an%20exception%20was%20for%20Malaviya%2C%20a%20hardcore%20Hindu%20nationalist%20from%20the%20Congress.%20This%20explains%20their%20ideological%20preference.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIt%20is%20laughable%20how%20Anant%20relies%20on%20a%20fig%20leaf%20of%20three%20pages%20but%20refuses%20to%20engage%20with%20deeper%20issues.%20He%20does%20not%20talk%20of%20how%20Poddar%20and%20Jaydayal%20Goyandka%20were%20among%20thousands%20who%20were%20apprehended%20on%20suspicion%20for%20involvement%20in%20Gandhi%20murder.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ENeither%20does%20he%20mention%20G.D.%20Birla%E2%80%99s%20refusal%20to%20help%20Poddar%20and%20Goyandka%20come%20out%20of%20jail.%20Birla%20succinctly%20called%20Poddar-Goyandka%20votaries%20of%20%E2%80%98%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3Eshaitan%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20dharma%20and%20not%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3Esanatan%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20dharma%E2%80%99.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWith%20both%20founders%20in%20jail%2C%20it%20is%20possible%20these%20three%20pages%20were%20glued%20to%20a%20few%20issues%20of%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3ENari%20Ank%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20to%20show%20their%20deep%20love%20for%20Gandhi.%20Even%20RSS%20chief%20M.S.%20Golwalkar%2C%20who%20was%20in%20Madras%2C%20sent%20frantic%20telegrams%20to%20Sardar%20Patel%2C%20Jawaharlal%20Nehru%20and%20Devdas%20Gandhi%20condemning%20Gandhi%E2%80%99s%20assassination%20on%20the%20evening%20of%20the%20murder.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ENow%2C%20it%20has%20been%20squarely%20proved%20by%20Dhirendra%20K.%20Jha%E2%80%99s%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EGandhi%E2%80%99s%20Assassin%3A%20The%20Making%20of%20Nathuram%20Godse%20and%20his%20Idea%20of%20India%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20(2021)%20that%20the%20killer%20Godse%20was%20from%20the%20RSS.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EFor%20Anant%2C%20it%20is%20also%20not%20important%20that%20Gita%20Press%20was%20opposed%20to%20temple-entry%20for%20Dalits%20and%20how%20this%20issue%20caused%20a%20major%20fracture%20in%20the%20Gita%20Press-Gandhi%20relationship.%20Anant%20would%20also%20not%20know%20that%20when%20a%20big%20sex%20scandal%20took%20place%20in%20Gobind%20Bhavan%2C%20Gita%20Press%E2%80%99%20headquarters%20in%20Calcutta%2C%20it%20was%20Gandhi%20who%20came%20to%20their%20rescue.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIt%20will%20help%20Anant%20if%20he%20goes%20through%20the%20pages%20of%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EHindu%20Panch%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20and%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EChand%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20to%20see%20for%20himself%20how%20Gandhi%20helped.%20He%20should%20spend%20time%20in%20the%20archives%20rather%20than%20rely%20on%20poor%20evidence%20doled%20out%20by%20Gita%20Press.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20Read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fswallowing-gandhi-and-peace-in-one-prize%5C%22%3ESwallowing%20Gandhi%20and%20Peace%20in%20One%20Prize%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EJournalism%20and%20%3Cem%3EDainik%20Jagran%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOn%20July%2016%2C%20when%20Anant%20Vijay%E2%80%99s%20half-baked%20column%20appeared%2C%20I%20immediately%20contacted%20Sanjay%20Gupta%2C%20the%20newspaper%E2%80%99s%20CEO%3B%20Vishnu%20Prakash%20Tripathi%2C%20editor%3B%20and%20Rajiv%20Sachan%2C%20editor%2C%20edit%20page.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EI%20requested%20them%20to%20publish%20my%20rejoinder%2C%20a%20common%20practice%20in%20journalism.%20For%20hours%20there%20was%20no%20response.%20Later%20in%20the%20day%2C%20Sachan%20sent%20a%20message%20that%20someone%20from%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EJagran%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20will%20contact%20me.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOn%20July%2017%2C%20a%20call%20came%20from%20Arun%20Srivastava%2C%20senior%20editor%20in%20the%20features%20department%2C%20asking%20me%20what%20my%20objections%20were.%20I%20explained%20to%20him%20in%20detail.%20He%20sounded%20convinced%20and%20promised%20to%20get%20back.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHe%20did%20not%20call%20the%20next%20day.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOn%20July%2019%2C%20I%20called%20Srivastava%2C%20who%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CThere%20is%20%5Ba%5D%20lack%20of%20unanimity%20in%20%5Bthe%5D%20office%20about%20publishing%20the%20rejoinder.%E2%80%9D%20In%20the%2024%20years%20of%20my%20career%20as%20a%20journalist%2C%20this%20is%20the%20first%20time%20I%20heard%20something%20like%20this.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAgain%2C%20I%20sent%20another%20set%20of%20messages%20to%20Gupta%2C%20Tripathi%20and%20Sachan.%20Like%20on%20the%20first%20day%2C%20Gupta%20and%20Tripathi%20did%20not%20bother%20to%20reply.%20Sachan%20sent%20a%20cryptic%20one%20liner%2C%20%E2%80%9CYou%20should%20talk%20to%20Mr%20Sanjay%20Gupta.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20July%2020%2C%20hours%20after%20the%20piece%20was%20sent%20to%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20Sachan%20sent%20a%20message%20asking%20for%20my%20response%20in%20400%20to%20500%20words.%20We%20spoke.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20Anant%20will%20respond%20to%20my%20rejoinder.%20I%20requested%20that%20I%20also%20be%20allowed%20to%20write.%20Sachan%20said%20it%20is%20not%20possible.%20He%20also%20said%20the%20paper%20plays%20back%20the%20edited%20version%20only%20if%20something%20is%20added%2C%20not%20otherwise.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EI%20decided%20to%20stay%20with%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fauthor%2Fakshaya-mukul%5C%22%3EAkshaya%20Mukul%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0is%20a%20Delhi-based%20journalist%20and%20author%20of%3C%2Fem%3E%C2%A0Gita%20Press%20and%20the%20Making%20of%20Hindu%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1689855351000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F20154759%2FGPMG.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fgita-press-gandhi-anant-vijay%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%20rejoinder%20to%20Dainik%20Jagran%20journalist%20Anant%20Vijay's%20reasoning%20for%20why%20reprints%20of%20a%20Kalyan%20edition%20did%20not%20carry%20an%20obituary%20of%20Gandhi.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fgita-press-gandhi-anant-vijay%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Govt%20bans%20exports%20of%20non-basmati%20white%20rice%20to%20boost%20domestic%20supply%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1689855248000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fbsmedia.business-standard.com%2F_media%2Fbs%2Fimg%2Farticle%2F2023-04%2F11%2Ffull%2F1681187131-807