l%20Kashmir%E2%80%99s%20Chrari%20Sharief%2C%20when%20he%20was%20out%20on%20a%20routine%20patrol%20in%20a%20forest%20in%20Sangerwani%20area%20of%20south%20Kashmir%E2%80%99s%20Pulwama%20district%20on%20Tuesday%20(July%2018)%20night.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20family%20member%20said%20that%20the%20victim%20was%20rushed%20to%20a%20local%20hospital.%20Doctors%20at%20the%20hospital%20referred%20him%20to%20Srinagar%20for%20specialised%20treatment%20where%20he%20succumbed%20to%20his%20injuries%20on%20Wednesday%2C%20%E2%80%9CHe%20had%20suffered%20a%20lethal%20bullet%20injury%20in%20his%20thigh.%20By%20the%20time%20he%20was%20taken%20to%20hospital%2C%20he%20had%20lost%20a%20lot%20of%20blood%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20family%20member%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJahangir%20Ahmed%20Chechi%2C%20a%20forester%20who%20was%20part%20of%20the%20patrolling%20party%2C%20was%20injured%20in%20the%20shooting%20but%20his%20condition%20is%20reported%20to%20be%20stable.%20The%20J%26amp%3BK%20Police%20said%20it%20was%20a%20%E2%80%9Cterror%20crime%E2%80%9D%20but%20didn%E2%80%99t%20specify%20the%20details%20of%20those%20involved%20in%20the%20shooting.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CDuring%20the%20search%20of%20the%20scene%20of%20crime%2C%20two%20empty%20fired%20cartridges%20of%20Ak-47%20ammunition%20and%20one%20bullet%20head%20was%20recovered%20from%20the%20spot.%20However%2C%20the%20search%20operation%20is%20going%20on%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20a%20police%20statement%2C%20adding%20that%20a%20case%20has%20been%20filed%20under%20Sections%2016%20and%2020%20of%20the%20Unlawful%20Activities%20Prevention%20Act%2C%20302%20of%20Indian%20Penal%20Code%20and%207%2F27%20Arms%20Act.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20the%20news%20of%20his%20death%20broke%2C%20a%20pall%20of%20gloom%20descended%20in%20the%20area%20with%20hundreds%20of%20people%2C%20including%20government%20officials%2C%20visiting%20the%20residence%20to%20express%20solidarity%20with%20his%20family.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20victim%20was%20working%20as%20a%20casual%20worker%20in%20J%26amp%3BK%E2%80%99s%20forest%20department.%20He%20is%20survived%20by%20his%20ailing%20parents%20%E2%80%93%20his%20father%2C%20Mohd%20Yusuf%20Wani%2C%20has%20an%20injured%20spine%20%E2%80%93%20and%20an%20unmarried%20sister.%20His%20other%2C%20older%20sister%20and%20elder%20brother%20are%20both%20married%20and%20they%20live%20separately.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20told%20him%20to%20stay%20back%20and%20not%20go%20out%20at%20night.%20But%20he%20refused%2C%20saying%20that%20some%20timber%20smugglers%20were%20planning%20to%20cut%20down%20trees%20in%20the%20forest%20and%20he%20had%20to%20stop%20them.%20We%20don%E2%80%99t%20know%20who%20killed%20him%20or%20why%20but%20his%20death%20has%20robbed%20us%20of%20our%20only%20support%20in%20old%20age%2C%E2%80%9D%20Yusuf%2C%20Imran%E2%80%99s%20father%2C%20told%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%20over%20the%20phone.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20attack%20took%20place%20barely%20hours%20after%20two%20migrant%20workers%20were%20shot%20by%20suspected%20terrorists%20in%20south%20Kashmir%E2%80%99s%20Anantnag%20district%20on%20Tuesday%20evening.%20Officials%20said%20that%20the%20victims%20%E2%80%93%20identified%20as%20Akshay%2C%2020%2C%20and%20Saurav%2C%2020%2C%20both%20residents%20of%20Maharashtra%E2%80%99s%20Sangli%20%E2%80%93%20survived%20the%20attack%20and%20their%20condition%20was%20stable.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELast%20week%2C%20three%20migrant%20workers%20were%20shot%20and%20injured%20in%20a%20similar%20attack%20in%20Gagren%20village%20of%20the%20adjoining%20Shopian%20district%20on%20July%2013%20evening.%20The%20victims%2C%20identified%20as%20Anmol%20Kumar%2C%20Pintu%20Kumar%20and%20Heeralal%20Yadav%2C%20residents%20of%20Supaul%20in%20Bihar%2C%20suffered%20bullet%20injuries.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThey%20are%20presently%20undergoing%20treatment%20at%20a%20hospital%20in%20Srinagar.%20Their%20condition%20is%20stable%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20an%20official%20in%20the%20J%26amp%3BK%20administration%20who%20didn%E2%80%99t%20want%20to%20be%20named.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFollowing%20the%20attack%2C%20the%20J%26amp%3BK%20Police%20had%20shunted%20out%20Station%20House%20Officer%20of%20Shopian%20police%20station%2C%20Ghulam%20Jeelani%20Bhat%2C%20and%20an%20inquiry%20was%20ordered.%20%E2%80%9CIn%20view%20of%20the%20incident%E2%80%A6..%2C%20Inspector%20Gh%20Jeelani%20Bhat%20(AWP)%20(SHO%20P%2FS%20Shopian)%20PID%20No%20ARP-109258%2C%20is%20attached%20to%20RPHQ%20Anantnag%20pending%20inquiry%2C%E2%80%9D%20an%20order%20by%20J%26amp%3BK%20Police%20stated.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJ%26amp%3BK%20National%20Conference%20leader%20and%20Lok%20Sabha%20Member%20of%20Parliament%20Hasnain%20Masoodi%20said%20that%20the%20attacks%20raise%20questions%20about%20the%20claims%20of%20the%20Union%20government%20and%20J%26amp%3BK%20administration%20that%20militancy%20has%20been%20eliminated%20from%20Kashmir.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9COur%20party%20leadership%20condemns%20violence%20in%20all%20forms.%20However%2C%20these%20attacks%20also%20raise%20questions%20which%20debunk%20the%20government%E2%80%99s%20narrative%20that%20all%20is%20well%20and%20normalcy%20has%20been%20restored%20in%20Kashmir%2C%E2%80%9D%20Masoodi%2C%20a%20former%20judge%20of%20the%20J%26amp%3BK%20high%20court%2C%20told%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20string%20of%20attacks%20took%20place%20at%20a%20time%20when%20the%20State%20Investigation%20Agency%20of%20the%20J%26amp%3BK%20Police%20has%20stepped%20up%20a%20probe%20into%20the%20killing%20of%20Sanjay%20Kumar%20Sharma%2C%20a%20Kashmir%20Pandit%2C%20who%20was%20shot%20dead%20outside%20his%20home%20in%20Pulwama%20district%20on%20February%2026%2C%20the%20first%20such%20incident%20this%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20SIA%2C%20which%20was%20formed%20on%20the%20lines%20of%20the%20National%20Investigation%20Agency%20for%20probing%20terrorism%20cases%20in%20J%26amp%3BK%20after%20Article%20370%20was%20read%20down%2C%20raided%20the%20residence%20of%20three%20active%20militants%20in%20Shopian%20district%20among%2010%20premises%20in%20three%20districts%20of%20south%20Kashmir%20earlier%20this%20week.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20raids%20were%20carried%20out%20in%20connection%20with%20the%20killing%20of%20Sharma%2C%20who%20worked%20as%20a%20guard%20at%20an%20ATM%20in%20his%20native%20Achan%20village.%20The%20agency%20said%20that%20it%20has%20identified%20the%20perpetrator%20involved%20in%20the%20killing%20of%20Sharma.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20hinterland%20in%20Kashmir%20has%20registered%20an%20uptick%20in%20violence%20over%20the%20past%20week%2C%20the%20Line%20of%20Control%20has%20also%20heated%20up%2C%20with%20security%20agencies%20claiming%20to%20have%20gunned%20down%20at%20least%20six%20unidentified%20militants%20in%20two%20encounters%20in%20the%20frontier%20Poonch%20district%20of%20Pir%20Panjal%20region.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFollowing%20the%20reading%20down%20of%20Article%20370%2C%20the%20Pir%20Panjal%20region%2C%20which%20falls%20along%20the%20Line%20of%20Control%20in%20Jammu%20division%2C%20has%20witnessed%20a%20revival%20of%20militancy%20in%20recent%20years%2C%20with%20the%20Army%20suffering%20nearly%20two%20dozen%20casualties%20in%20the%20past%20two%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20deadly%20attacks%20have%20prompted%20the%20authorities%20to%20launch%20%E2%80%98Operation%20Trinetra%E2%80%99%20for%20taking%20out%20militants%20who%20are%20believed%20to%20be%20hiding%20in%20the%20forested%20areas%20of%20Pir%20Panjal%20districts%20of%20Poonch%20and%20Rajouri.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFour%20of%20the%20six%20militants%20in%20Poonch%20were%20killed%20on%20Tuesday%20under%20this%20operation%2C%20with%20the%20Army%20claiming%20to%20have%20recovered%20weapons%20reportedly%20made%20in%20China%20and%20Pakistan%20from%20the%20encounter%20site%20along%20with%20other%20arms%20and%20ammunition.%20Two%20more%20unidentified%20militants%20were%20also%20gunned%20down%20in%20north%20Kashmir%E2%80%99s%20Kupwara%20district%20on%20Wednesday.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22publ