-lankas-tamil-lawmakers-ask-modi-to-pressurise-wickremsinghe-on-devolution-during-india-visit%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Ewrote%20an%20open%20letter%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20to%20Modi%20asking%20him%20to%20urge%20Wickremesinghe%20to%20meet%20commitments%20under%20the%20Indo-Lanka%20accord%20to%20devolve%20police%20and%20revenue%20powers%20to%20the%20provinces.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EA%20day%20later%2C%20Wickremesinghe%20met%20with%20Sri%20Lankan%20Tamil%20lawmakers%2C%20but%20it%20was%20clear%20that%20there%20was%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Feconomynext.com%2Fsri-lanka-president-tamil-national-alliance-mps-disagree-on-police-powers-126176%2F%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Eno%20bridging%20the%20gaps%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20between%20the%20two%20sides.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fsouth-asia%2Fsri-lankas-tamil-lawmakers-ask-modi-to-pressurise-wickremsinghe-on-devolution-during-india-visit%5C%22%3ESri%20Lanka%E2%80%99s%20Tamil%20Lawmakers%20Ask%20Modi%20to%20Pressurise%20Wickremsinghe%20on%20Devolution%20During%20India%20Visit%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESources%20told%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20that%20India%20will%20articulate%20the%20standard%20positions%20on%20the%20full%20implementation%20of%20the%2013%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3Eth%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%20amendment.%20However%2C%20there%20is%20not%20much%20expectation%20from%20New%20Delhi%20that%20Wickremesinghe%20holds%20the%20political%20clout%20to%20move%20the%20needle%20on%20this%20sensitive%20subject%2C%20said%20a%20person%20involved%20in%20the%20discussions.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWickremesinghe%20is%20the%20sole%20member%20of%20parliament%20from%20his%20party%2C%20UNP%2C%20who%20is%20supported%20by%20the%20Rajapaksas%E2%80%99%20Sri%20Lanka%20Podujana%20Peramuna%20(SLPP).%20%E2%80%9CEven%20if%20he%20has%20the%20genuine%20political%20will%2C%20he%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20have%20the%20mandate%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20a%20source.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHowever%2C%20New%20Delhi%20hopes%20that%20Wickremesinghe%20will%20have%20more%20scope%20for%20moving%20forward%20on%20Indian%20development%20projects.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThere%20has%20always%20been%20a%20bit%20of%20disappointment%20with%20Wickremesinghe%20in%20New%20Delhi%20as%20many%20Indian%20projects%20were%20stuck%20during%20his%20stint%20as%20prime%20minister%20under%20the%20Maithripala%20Sirisena%20presidency.%20India%20had%20hoped%20that%20Sirisena%2C%20who%20succeeded%20Gotabaya%20Rajapaksa%2C%20would%20be%20friendlier%20to%20Indian%20interests%20and%20keep%20China%20at%20bay.%20It%20had%20also%20accordingly%20tempered%20its%20position%20on%20the%20reconciliation%20issue%20to%20not%20politically%20rock%20the%20government.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBut%2C%20the%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fdiplomacy%2Findia-sri-lanka-talks-modi-wickremesinghe%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Eopen%20bickering%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20between%20Sirisena%20and%20Wickremesinghe%20meant%20there%20was%20hardly%20any%20progress%20on%20any%20of%20the%20projects.%20During%20Wickremesinghe%E2%80%99s%20visit%20to%20India%20as%20prime%20minister%20in%202018%2C%20the%20Indian%20side%20had%20a%20general%20line%20that%20the%20progress%20on%20projects%20were%20%E2%80%98reviewed%E2%80%99.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHowever%2C%20there%20was%20no%20such%20diplomatese%20from%20Wickremesinghe%E2%80%99s%20office%2C%20which%20issued%20a%20statement%20that%20the%20Indian%20prime%20minister%20had%20%E2%80%9Cexpressed%20his%20discontent%20over%20the%20response%20of%20the%20Sri%20Lankan%20government%20towards%20the%20assistance%20given%20by%20India%E2%80%9D.%20It%20was%20largely%20seen%20as%20an%20effort%20to%20put%20the%20blame%20entirely%20on%20Sirisena%20and%20take%20away%20any%20pressure%20on%20him%20from%20New%20Delhi%20for%20the%20slow%20pace%20of%20work.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fsouth-asia%2Findia-should-set-a-timeframe-for-sri-lanka-to-implement-the-indo-sri-lanka-accord%5C%22%3EIndia%20Should%20Set%20a%20Timeframe%20For%20Sri%20Lanka%20to%20Implement%20the%20Indo-Sri%20Lanka%20Accord%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAt%20the%20time%2C%20the%20major%20point%20of%20contention%20was%20the%20East%20Container%20Terminal%20at%20Colombo%20port%20which%20had%20been%20given%20to%20India%20and%20Japan.%20It%20was%20seen%20by%20India%20as%20a%20strategic%20move%20especially%20with%20China%20developing%20the%20Colombo%20International%20Container%20Terminal.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAfter%20the%20Rajapaksas%20were%20back%20at%20the%20helm%2C%20Sri%20Lanka%20unilaterally%20terminated%20the%20tripartite%20agreement.%20In%20October%202021%2C%20Adani%20Group%20signed%20a%20deal%2C%20which%20was%20largely%20seen%20as%20a%20compromise%2C%20to%20develop%20the%20West%20Container%20terminal.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESince%20he%20took%20over%20as%20President%20last%20year%2C%20Wickremesinghe%20has%20been%20battling%20the%20economic%20crisis%20with%20Sri%20Lanka%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bloomberg.com%2Fnews%2Farticles%2F2022-05-19%2Fsri-lanka-enters-default-and-warns-inflation-may-surge-to-40%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Edefaulting%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20on%20its%20foreign%20debt%20for%20the%20first%20time.%20It%20had%20been%20a%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fdiplomacy%2Fsri-lanka-chinese-ship-hambantota-tourism%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Erocky%20start%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20especially%20over%20the%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fdiplomacy%2Famid-indias-pressure-sri-lanka-urges-china-to-defer-visit-of-its-ship-to-hambantota-report%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Evisit%20by%20a%20Chinese%20ship%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20but%20India%20has%20offered%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Feconomictimes.indiatimes.com%2Fnews%2Findia%2Findia-extends-1-billion-credit-line-for-sri-lanka-by-a-year%2Farticleshow%2F100098046.cms%3Ffrom%3Dmdr%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Enearly%20%244%20billion%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20in%20financial%20assistance%20to%20Sri%20Lanka%20during%20this%20crisis.%20However%2C%20New%20Delhi%E2%80%99s%20purse%20strings%20are%20not%20open%20any%20more.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIndian%20officials%20believe%20that%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.imf.org%2Fen%2FNews%2FArticles%2F2023%2F03%2F20%2Fpr2379-imf-executive-board-approves-under-the-new-eff-arrangement-for-sri-lanka%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EIMF%E2%80%99s%20approval%20of%20a%20%243%20billion%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20loan%20has%20opened%20doors%20for%20other%20funding%20channels%20and%20the%20situation%20has%20stabilised%2C%20giving%20Wickremesinghe%20the%20space%20to%20look%20at%20other%20issues.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAs%20per%20sources%2C%20there%20is%20an%20expectation%20that%20Wickremesinghe%20will%20move%20faster%20on%20India-related%20projects%20as%20he%20is%20unlikely%20to%20face%20much%20domestic%20pushback%20on%20the%20issue%20this%20time.%20There%20is%20no%20likelihood%20of%20the%20parliament%20being%20dissolved%20for%20an%20election%20any%20time%20soon%2C%20with%20most%20lawmakers%20from%20the%20ruling%20coalition%20expected%20to%20lose%20their%20seats.%20Announcements%20on%20accelerating%20flagship%20Indian%20projects%20after%20the%20main%20talks%20on%20Friday%20are%20likely.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EChina%20is%20Sri%20Lanka%E2%80%99s%20largest%20bilateral%20creditor%2C%20with%20whom%20it%20is%20in%20the%20midst%20of%20debt-restructuring%20talks.%20Therefore%2C%20it%20would%20be%20difficult%20to%20visualise%20that%20Colombo%20will%20take%20any%20steps%20that%20will%20annoy%20Beijing%20%E2%80%93%20or%20for%20that%20matter%2C%20India%2C%20at%20this%20crucial%20juncture.%20Sri%20Lanka%20will%20likely%20walk%20a%20fine%20line%20between%20the%20two%20countries%2C%20without%20alienating%20either.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EFor%20India%2C%20the%20focus%20for%20Wickremesinghe%E2%80%99s%20visit%20is%20on%20connectivity%2C%20with%20greater%20integration%20with%20the%20Indian%20economy%20as%20the%20underlying%20theme.%20Sources%20pointed%20out%20that%20there%20is%20potential%20for%20more%20sea%20and%20air%20links%20between%20the%20two%20countries%2C%20and%20digitization%20of%20financial%20transactions%20would%20also%20be%20added%20to%20that%20package.%20%E2%80%9CIndians%20are%20already%20the%20largest%20source%20for%20tourism%20in%20Sri%20Lanka.%20More%20links%20will%20only%20boost%20that%20sector%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20an%20official.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAs%20per%20official%20figures%2C%20India%E2%80%99s%20overall%20trade%20volume%20in%202021%20was%20%245.4%20billion%20%E2%80%93%20an%20increase%20of%2048%25%20from%20the%20pandemic%20year%20of%202020.%20China%20has%20also%20emerged%20as%20Sri%20Lanka%E2%80%99s%20top%20trading%20partner%20in%20recent%20years.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIndia%20has%20also%20been%20keen%20to%20revive%20talks%20for%20an%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.adaderana.lk%2Fnews.php%3Fnid%3D86737%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EEconomic%20and%20Technological%20Cooperation%20Agreement%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20(ETCA)%20with%20Sri%20Lanka%2C%20which%20will%20expand%20an%20existing%20free%20trade%20agreement%20(FTA)%20that%20had%20begun%20and%20stalled%20during%20the%20Sirisena%20presidency.%20This%20will%20certainly%20be%20on%20the%20agenda%2C%20sources%20confirmed%2C%20with%20India%20having%20revised%20its%20position%20on%20FTAs%20and%20signed%20a%20slew%20of%20them%2