tly%20opposing%20his%20bail%E2%80%A6%20neither%20are%20we%20supporting%20it.%20We%20leave%20it%20to%20the%20wisdom%20of%20the%20Court%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20news%20outlet%20reported%20the%20Delhi%20Police%20as%20saying.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20July%2018%2C%20the%20court%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpreview%2F664177%5C%22%3Egranted%3C%2Fa%3E%20him%20and%20Vinod%20Tomar%2C%20the%20suspended%20WFI%20assistant%20secretary%2C%20a%20two-day%20interim%20bail%20till%20Thursday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETomar%20has%20also%20been%20granted%20regular%20bail%20in%20the%20case.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOlympic-level%20wrestlers%20were%20forced%20to%20hold%20a%20protest%20against%20him%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewirehindi.com%2F237863%2Ftop-wrestlers-accuses-bjp-mp-wfi-chiefbrij-bhushan-sharan-singh-and-coaches-of-sexual-harassment%2F%5C%22%3Estaging%20a%20dharna%3C%2Fa%3E%20at%20Delhi%E2%80%99s%20Jantar%20Mantar%20from%20January%2018.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBajrang%20Punia%2C%20Sakshi%20Malik%2C%20and%20Asian%20Games%20champion%20Vinesh%20Phogat%2C%20were%20among%20the%20protesters%20demanding%20Singh%E2%80%99s%20arrest.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESingh%20has%20consistently%20rejected%20all%20allegations%20of%20misconduct.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Delhi%20Police%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fdelhi-police-brij-bhushan-bjp-mp-wrestlers-chargesheet%5C%22%3Ehad%20filed%3C%2Fa%3E%20a%20charge-sheet%20against%20the%20six-time%20MP%20on%20June%2015%20under%20sections%20354%20(assault%20or%20criminal%20force%20to%20woman%20with%20intent%20to%20outrage%20her%20modesty)%2C%20354A%20(sexual%20harassment)%2C%20354D%20(stalking)%20and%20506%20(criminal%20intimidation)%20of%20the%20Indian%20Penal%20Code%20(IPC).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETomar%20was%20charged%20with%20offences%20under%20IPC%20sections%20109%20(abetment%20of%20any%20offence%2C%20if%20the%20act%20abetted%20is%20committed%20in%20consequence%2C%20and%20where%20no%20