hase%20warplanes%20and%20deadly%20submarines.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThat%20is%20hardly%20a%20task%20that%20a%20mere%20defence%20minister%2C%20however%20adroit%20and%20worth%20her%20aggressive%20salt%2C%20could%20have%20been%20trusted%20to%20engage%20in.%20What%20if%20the%20defence%20minister%20had%20returned%20home%20with%20duds%2C%20not%20knowing%20that%20she%20had%20been%20taken%20for%20a%20Parisian%20ride%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMore%20significantly%2C%20it%20had%20to%20be%20the%20freedom-loving%20Shri%20Modi%20who%20could%20best%20grace%20an%20occasion%20that%20saw%20the%20birth%20of%20the%20idea%20of%20democracy%20in%20the%20world%2C%20namely%2C%20Bastille%20Day%2C%20dating%20back%20to%20July%2014%2C%201789%2C%20when%20the%20long-ruling%20Bourbon%20monarchy%20of%20France%20was%20challenged%20by%20the%20plebs%20through%20their%20protest%20at%20the%20Bastille%20prison%2C%20in%20the%20course%20of%20which%20some%20political%20prisoners%20were%20released.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWho%20other%20than%20Shri%20Modi%20among%20world%20leaders%20would%20have%20better%20understood%20the%20progressive%20import%20of%20that%20occurrence%2C%20given%20that%20most%20are%20nowadays%20busy%20warding%20off%20such%20protests%20at%20home%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhich%20reminds%20us%3A%20what%20a%20pity%20that%20our%20liberatory%20prime%20minister%20should%20not%20have%20been%20with%20his%20beloved%20Kashmiris%20on%20a%20day%20just%20before%20Bastille%20Day%2C%20namely%2C%20July%2013%2C%20which%20in%201931%20marked%20the%20beginning%20of%20democratic%20stirrings%20in%20the%20then%20monarchical%20state%20of%20Jammu%20%26amp%3B%20Kashmir.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20that%20day%20as%20well%2C%20Kashmiri%20plebs%20had%20protested%20outside%20a%20prison%20in%20Srinagar%20to%20seek%20the%20release%20of%20a%20political%20prisoner%2C%20only%20to%20see%20some%2021%20of%20the%20protesters%20shot%20dead%20by%20the%20King%E2%80%99s%20police.%20Had%C2%A0%20Shri%20Modi%20been%20with%20us%2C%20Kashmiris%20wishing%20to%20pay%20homage%20to%20the%20martyrs%20of%20that%20day%2C%20as%20they%20have%20routinely%20done%20through%20the%20years%2C%20would%20not%20have%20been%20autocratically%20prevented%20from%20engaging%20in%20that%20commemorative%20act.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIs%20it%20not%20remarkable%20that%20the%20liberation%20of%20the%20Bastille%20followed%20just%20a%20day%20after%20the%20attempt%20to%20liberate%20a%20prison%20in%20Srinagar%2C%20though%20centuries%20apart%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20are%20wags%20in%20our%20republic%20who%20routinely%20fault%20the%20beloved%20prime%20minister%20for%20saying%20what%20he%20says%2C%20and%20not%20saying%20what%20he%20does%20not%3B%20or%20for%20being%20where%20he%20is%2C%20and%20not%20being%20where%20he%20should%20be.%20Thus%2C%20a%20great%20brouhaha%20has%20been%20afloat%20about%20how%20Shri%20Modi%20did%20not%20choose%20to%20commiserate%20with%20our%20harassed%20women%20wrestlers%2C%20or%20berate%20the%20doughty%20offender%20who%20happens%20to%20be%20his%20own%20party%20subordinate.%20Likewise%2C%20Shri%20Modi%20is%20faulted%20for%20calling%20the%20oppositional%20kettle%20black%20with%20corruption%20while%20taking%20in%20the%20pot%20to%20bolster%20the%20prospects%20of%20the%20ruling%20party%2C%20as%20recently%20as%20in%20Maharashtra.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENeedless%20to%20say%2C%20these%20motivated%20denigrations%20remain%20ill-informed%20in%20the%20extreme%20about%20the%20sophistications%20that%20good%20governance%20at%20the%20very%20top%20requires%20of%20a%20numero%20uno%2C%20if%20the%20republic%20is%20not%20to%20be%20consigned%20to%20the%20corroding%20effects%20of%20petty%20morality%C2%A0%20and%20shallow%20justice.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20it%20is%2C%20no%20Indian%20prime%20minister%20has%20ever%20been%20as%20much%20everywhere%2C%20both%20in%20person%20and%20via%20posters%2C%20as%20Shri%20Modi.%20It%20seems%20that%20greedy%20Modi-lovers%20would%20not%20mind%20if%20half%20a%20dozen%20clones%20of%20the%20great%20leader%20were%20to%20be%20forged%20through%20the%20exercise%20of%20Artificial%20Intelligence%2C%20so%20that%20it%20might%20seem%20to%20the%20public%20view%20that%20the%20central%20cabinet%20had%20but%20a%20Modi%20in%20all%20places.%20This%20would%20help%20make%20rousingly%20visible%20a%20fact%20which%20exists%20but%20only%20insufficiently%20to%20the%20satisfaction%20of%20the%20devoted%C2%A0%20groupie.%20Just%20goes%20to%20show%20what%20price%C2%A0%20an%20outstanding%20leader%20pays%20for%20being%20subject%20to%20the%20constraints%20of%20time%20and%20space.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fauthor%2Fbadri-raina%5C%22%3EBadri%20Raina%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0taught%20at%20Delhi%20University.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1689851410000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F20163435%2FH20230714135299.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Funeasy-lies-the-head-of-government-bounded-by-time-and-space%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22No%20Indian%20prime%20minister%20has%20ever%20been%20as%20much%20everywhere%2C%20both%20in%20person%20and%20via%20posters%2C%20as%20Shri%20Modi.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A5%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Funeasy-lies-the-head-of-government-bounded-by-time-and-space%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22G20%20Finance%20Ministers%20Meet%20Falls%20Short%20of%20Endorsing%20Report%20on%20Multilateral%20Development%20Banks%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F20153526%2FF1UTpZNX0AEvOtn.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EA%20report%20on%20reforming%20the%20multilateral%20development%20banks%20(MDBs)%2C%20by%20an%20independent%20expert%20group%2C%20has%20not%20yet%20received%20the%20endorsement%20of%20the%20G20%20finance%20ministers.%20It%20appears%20the%20report%2C%20authored%20by%20N.K.%20Singh%20and%20Lawrence%20Summers%2C%20may%20not%20get%20a%20go-ahead%20during%20India%E2%80%99s%20G-20%20presidency.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20third%20G20%20finance%20ministers%20and%20Central%20Bank%20Governors%20(FMCBG)%20held%20in%20Gandhinagar%20on%20July%2017-18%20did%20not%20accept%20the%20recommendations%20of%20the%20expert%20group.%20Instead%2C%20the%20members%20said%20that%20they%20%E2%80%9Cmay%20choose%20to%20discuss%E2%80%9D%20the%20recommendations%20to%20%E2%80%9Cenhance%20their%20effectiveness%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Feconomy%2Fnews%2Fthird-g20-fmcbg-meeting-fails-to-endorse-report-on-reforming-mdbs-123071901015_1.html%5C%22%3EAccording%20to%20%3Cem%3EBusiness%20Standard%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20a%20senior%20G20%20delegate%20from%20India%2C%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CWe%20are%20disappointed%20that%20the%20recommendations%20of%20the%20MDB%20reforms%20report%20were%20not%20endorsed%20in%20the%20chair%E2%80%99s%20summary%20released%20in%20Gandhinagar.%20It%20was%20only%20taken%20note%20of.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20address%20global%20challenges%20of%20the%2021st%20century%2C%20G20%20members%20recognised%20the%20importance%20of%20strengthening%20MDBs%20and%20to%20let%20its%20ecosystem%20evolve.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fpib.gov.in%2FPressReleaseIframePage.aspx%3FPRID%3D1940536%23%3A~%3Atext%3DThe%2520Third%2520G20%2520Finance%2520Ministers%2CFinance%2520and%2520Corporate%2520Affairs%2520Smt.%5C%22%3Epress%20statement%3C%2Fa%3E%20by%20India%E2%80%99s%20finance%20ministry%20merely%20acknowledged%20the%20prepared%20report%20without%20commenting%20on%20why%20it%20was%20not%20endorsed%2C%20as%20was%20expected.%20%E2%80%9CMembers%20appreciated%20the%20efforts%20of%20the%20G20%20Independent%20Expert%20Group%20on%20Strengthening%20MDBs%20constituted%20by%20the%20Indian%20Presidency%20earlier%20this%20year.%C2%A0%20The%20Expert%20Group%20has%20prepared%20Volume%201%20of%20the%20Report%2C%20and%20Volume%202%20is%20expected%20in%20October%202023.%20Noting%20Volume%201%E2%80%99s%20recommendations%2C%20members%20shared%20that%20the%20MDBs%20may%20choose%20to%20discuss%20these%20recommendations%20to%20enhance%20their%20effectiveness%2C%E2%80%9D%20it%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20report%20co-authored%20by%20the%20chairman%20of%2015th%20Finance%20Commission%2C%20N.K.%20Singh%2C%20stresses%20on%20the%20greater%20engagement%20with%20private%20sector%20for%20MDBs.%20It%20notes%20that%20private%20financing%20worth%20%24740%20billion%20per%20year%20will%20be%20required%20to%20reach%20overall%20goals%20for%20additional%20climate%20and%20sustainable%20development%20goals%20(SDGs)-related%20finance%2C%20an%20increase%20of%20%24500%20billion%20over%20the%202019%20level%20of%20sovereign%20borrowing%20and%20private%20participation%20in%20infrastructure%2C%20the%20%3Cem%3EIndian%20Express%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Findianexpress.com%2Farticle%2Fbusiness%2Fg20-expert-group-on-mdbs-suggests-greater-engagement-with-private-sector-8849164%2F%5C%22%3Ereported%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CToday%2C%20MDBs%20only%20mobilise%200.6%20dollars%20in%20private%20capital%20for%20each%20dollar%20they%20lend%20on%20their%20own%20account.%20They%20should%20aim%20to%20at%20least%20double%20this%20target%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20report%20argues.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20also%20calls%20for%20better%20coordination%20between%20MDBs%2C%20noting%20that%20while%20some%20MDBs%20have%20been%20leaner%20and%20faster%20(AIIB)%2C%20others%20are%20experimenting%20with%20raising%20new%20forms%20of%20capital%20(AfDB%20and%20IDB)%2C%20engaging%20with%20the%20private%20sector%20(EBRD%20and%20IFC)%20or%20better%20utilising%20their%20balance%20sheets%20in%20other%20ways%20(IBRD%20and%20ADB).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20report%20also%20goes%20onto%20to%20add%20that%20a%20%E2%80%98triple%20mandate%E2%80%99%20is%20required%20to%20address%20poverty%2C%20inclusive%20growth%20and%20the%20financing%20of%20global%20public%20goods.%20These%2C%20the%20reports%20says%2C%20can%20be%20made%20possible%20by%20tripling%20the%20level%20of%20financing%20commitments%20and%20establishing%20a%20third%20funding%20mechanism.%20It%20further%20calls%20for%20the%20setting%20up%20of%20a%20%E2%80%98Global%20Challenges%20Funding%E2%80%99%20mechanism%20for%20%E2%80%98Global%20Public%20Goods%E2%80%99%2C%20for%20which%20the%20modalities%20will%20be%20detailed%20in%20the%20second%20volume%20of%20the%20report%20to%20be%20released%20later.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hindustantimes.com%2Findia-news%2Fus-supports-expansion-of-multilateral-development-banks-mandate-calls-for-reforms-and-greater-public-sector-engagement-101689532022700.html%5C%22%3EAccording%20to%20%3Cem%3EHindustan%20Times%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20several%20factors%20have%20come%20together%20to%20make%20MDB%20reform%20a%20%E2%80%9Cpressing%20agenda%E2%80%9D.%20At%20the%20first%20level%2C%20there%20is%20an%20effort%20to%20expand%20the%20World%20Bank%E2%80%99s%20mandate%20from%20eliminating%20extreme%20poverty%20and%20boosting%20shared%20prosperity%20to%20addressing%20transboundary%20challenges%2C%20including%20the%20climate%20crisis.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWelcoming%20the%20report%2C%20US%20treasury%20secretary%2C%20Janet%20Yellen%2C%20had%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CThe%20World%20Bank%20is%20updating%20its%20mission%20statement%20and%20refreshing%20its%20operating%20model.%20And%20we%20are%20working%20with%20the%20World%20Bank%20and%20the%20regional%20development%20banks%20to%20implement%20measures%20that%20will%20more%20efficiently%20leverage%20the%20resources%20they%20have.%20Our%20reforms%20to%20the%20World%20Bank%E2%80%99s%20balance%20sheet%20will%20responsibly%20unlock%20as%20much%20as%20%2450%20billion%20in%20additional%20lending%20capacity%20over%20the%20next%20decade.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EYellen%20had%20further%20noted%20that%20MDB%20system%20can%20unlock%20%24200%20billion%20over%20the%20next%20decade%20just%20from%20the%20measures%20already%20being%20implemented%20or%20under%20deliberation%2C%20as%20a%20part%20of%20what%20is%20widely%20known%20as%20%E2%80%9Cbalance%20sheet%20optimisation%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWriting%20for%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Findianexpress.com%2Farticle%2Fopinion%2Fcolumns%2Findias-g20-presidency-multilateral-development-banks-pm-modi-us-visit-8687542%2F%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EIndian%20Express%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20N.K.%20Singh%20explained%20the%20importance%20of%20MDBs%20for%20the%20contemporary%20world.%C2%A0%E2%80%9COver%20the%20years%2C%20notwithstanding%20far-reaching%20geopolitical%20changes%2C%20economic%20crises%20and%20uncertainties%2C%20MDBs%20have%20remained%20relevant%20as%20credible%20institutions%20to%20support%20the%20development%20of%20both%20MICs%20%5BMiddle%20Income%20Countries%5D%20and%20LICs%20%5BLow%20Income%20Countries%5D.%20Yet%2C%20it%20is%20widely%20believed%20that%20these%20institutions%20are%20no%20longer%20suited%20in%20terms%20of%20the%20resources%2C%20cultural%20ethos%20and%20methods%20to%20address%20the%20emerging%20challenges.%20These%20relate%20to%20global%20public%20goods%2C%20climate%20change%20and%20pandemics.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20widely%20believed%20that%20MDBs%20are%20in%20a%20quagmire%2C%20trapped%20in%20their%20procedures%2C%20approach%20and%20methods%20of%20work%20and%20reticent%20to%20structural%20changes.%C2%A0Given%20their%20technical%20knowledge%2C%20experience%20and%20credibility%20in%20the%20financial%20sphere%2C%20they%20need%20to%20rediscover%20their%20role%20and%20methods.%20The%20two%20traditional%20goals%20shared%20by%20all%20multilateral%20institutions%20have%20been%20the%20elimination%20of%20poverty%20and%20fostering%20shared%20prosperity.%C2%A0The%20new%20challenge%20is%20to%20broaden%20the%20mandate%20and%20vision%20to%20address%20the%20challenges%20of%20transboundary%20issues